{"type":"message","id":"9c650296","parentId":"b243c012","timestamp":"2026-05-20T09:12:35.767Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to create a 1v1 client test requirement ticket on TAPD. Let me check the available skills for TAPD bug creation.\n\nFrom MEMORY.md, I know:\n- 需求单 = 1V1 需求单（2026-05-20）：主人说「提需求单」默认指提 **1V1 的需求单**，使用叶枝君的账号\n- 1V1需求单模板6种：client(客户端[12]+QA[16]+策划[14]), server(服务端[13]+QA[16]+策划[14]), design(策划[14]+QA[16]), ui(UI[7]+UI验收[8]+策划[14]+QA[16]), motion(2D动作[2]+策划[14]+QA[16]), audio(音频[11]+策划[14]+QA[16])\n\n\n- \"客户端测试需求单\" maps to the client template, but I'm missing the actual ticket details like title and description. I need to ask the user for these specifics before I can create the ticket.\n\nI should request the title, description, priority level, version, and module information.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"收到！需要知道需求单的基本信息才能提：\n\n- **标题**：需求叫什么？\n- **描述**：具体内容/背景是什么？\n- **优先级**：高/中/低？（默认中）\n- **版本**：要挂哪个版本？（默认不填）\n- **模块**：要挂哪个模块？（默认不填）\n\n子工作项会用 1V1 客户端模板：**客户端[12] + 策划[14] + QA[16]**，使用叶枝君的账号提。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779268343049,"responseId":"chatcmpl-3b63e475-c3bf-4395-89f1-ba85cbfa6af8"}}
