{"type":"message","id":"153efa05","parentId":"2c06207b","timestamp":"2026-05-20T09:23:09.011Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_016oBj9UgtxyqzZxrbQ9hTSh","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Trying: https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/stories/add?parent_id=1131253609001037866&workitem_type=CLIENT\n  Final URL: https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/stories/add?parent_id=1131253609001037866&workitem_type=CLIENT\n  Title: 创建需求-月圆之夜-TAPD平台\n  StoryName field exists: true\n  Parent field: NOT FOUND\nTrying: https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/stories/add?parent_id=1131253609001037866\n  Final URL: https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/stories/add?parent_id=1131253609001037866\n  Title: 创建需求-月圆之夜-TAPD平台\n  StoryName field exists: true\n  Parent field: NOT FOUND\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"vivid-sage","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"Trying: https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/stories/add?parent_id=1131253609001037866&workitem_type=CLIENT\n  Final URL: https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/stories/add?parent_id=1131253609001037866&workitem_type=CLIENT\n  Title: 创建需求-月圆之夜-TAPD平台\n  StoryName field exists: true\n  Parent field: NOT FOUND\nTrying: https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/stories/add?parent_id=1131253609001037866\n  Final URL: https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/stories/add?parent_id=1131253609001037866\n  Title: 创建需求-月圆之夜-TAPD平台\n  StoryName field exists: true\n  Parent field: NOT FOUND\n","name":"node scripts/test_substory_url.mjs"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1779268989011}}
{"type":"message","id":"e8bcf9c8","parentId":"153efa05","timestamp":"2026-05-20T09:23:26.924Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"URL 格式可以用！页面正常打开了，有 `StoryName` 字段。现在思路是：\n\n1. 创建主需求时清空 TemplateId（不带预设子工作项）\n2. 创建成功后，依次用 `parent_id=<STORY_ID>&workitem_type=CLIENT/DESIGN/QA` 创建3个子需求\n\n但需要知道 客户端/策划/QA 对应的 workitem_type 参数值。从之前的 HTML 看到了 `CLIENT`，让我确认其他的："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_vrtx_01AttNrDmGawZ53u77NuoHSE","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\inspect_workitem_types.mjs","content":"import { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\n\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(fileURLToPath(import.meta.url));\nconst WS_DIR = path.resolve(__dirname, '..');\nconst cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(path.join(WS_DIR, 'tapd_cookies_yezhijun.json'), 'utf8'));\n\nconst STORY_ID = '1131253609001037866';\nconst DETAIL_URL = `https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/stories/view/${STORY_ID}`;\n\nconst browser = await chromium.launch({ headless: false, args: ['--no-sandbox'] });\nconst context = await browser.newContext();\nawait context.addCookies(cookies);\nconst page = await context.newPage();\nawait page.goto(DETAIL_URL, { waitUntil: 'networkidle', timeout: 30000 });\nawait page.waitForTimeout(3000);\n\n// 直接从 HTML 里找所有 workitem_type 相关内容\nconst html = await page.content();\n\n// 找所有 workitemType / workitem_type 出现的地方\nconst regex = /workitem[_]?[Tt]ype['\":\\s=]+([A-Z_a-z0-9]+)/g;\nconst matches = [];\nlet m;\nwhile ((m = regex.exec(html)) !== null) {\n  matches.push(m[0].substring(0, 80));\n}\nconsole.log('WorkitemType occurrences:', matches.length);\nmatches.slice(0, 20).forEach(m => console.log(' ', m));\n\n// 找带 STORY/CLIENT/QA 字样的 span 附近内容\nconst spanTexts = html.match(/span[^>]*>[A-Z]{2,10}<\\/span><span>[^<]{2,20}<\\/span>/g) || [];\nconsole.log('\\nSpan pairs (icon + name):');\nspanTexts.slice(0, 20).forEach(t => console.log(' ', t));\n\n// 找 command=createSubStoryWithWorkitemType 的 li 里的完整内容\nconst liRegex = /command=\"createSubStoryWithWorkitemType\"[^>]*>.*?<\\/li>/gs;\nconst liMatches = html.match(liRegex) || [];\nconsole.log('\\nSub story type menu items:');\nliMatches.slice(0, 20).forEach(li => console.log(' ', li.substring(0, 200)));\n\nawait browser.close();\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779268989012,"responseId":"chatcmpl-c3b5528a-37d1-4f38-80ee-7b19e5e6f36e"}}
