pe occurrences: 0\n\nSpan pairs (icon + name):\n  span class=\"workitem-icon\" style=\"background-color: rgb(184, 233, 134);\">ARTSTORY</span><span>美术故事</span>\n  span class=\"workitem-icon\" style=\"background-color: rgb(201, 177, 81);\">ARTQA</span><span>美术验收</span>\n  span class=\"workitem-icon\" style=\"background-color: rgb(92, 136, 197);\">CLIENT</span><span>客户端</span>\n  span class=\"workitem-icon\" style=\"background-color: rgb(142, 190, 190);\">SERVERS</span><span>服务器</span>\n  span class=\"workitem-icon\" style=\"background-color: rgb(222, 113, 241);\">SPECIAL</span><span>特效</span>\n  span class=\"workitem-icon\" style=\"background-color: rgb(248, 94, 94);\">ORIGINAL</span><span>原画</span>\n  span class=\"workitem-icon\" style=\"background-color: rgb(147, 195, 107);\">AUDIO</span><span>音频</span>\n  span class=\"workitem-icon\" style=\"background-color: rgb(100, 193, 149);\">MASTER</span><span>策划</span>\n  span class=\"workitem-icon\" style=\"background-color: rgb(88, 86, 214);\">PATTERN</span><span>模型</span>\n  span class=\"workitem-icon\" style=\"background-color: rgb(178, 41, 34);\">ACTION</span><span>动作</span>\n  span class=\"workitem-icon\" style=\"background-color: rgb(238, 112, 161);\">QA</span><span>QA验收</span>\n\nSub story type menu items:\n  command=\"createSubStoryWithWorkitemType\" hide-on-click=\"\" class=\"agi-dropdown-menu-custom-item\"><span class=\"workitem-icon\" style=\"background-color: rgb(184, 233, 134);\">ARTSTORY</span><span>美术故事</spa\n  command=\"createSubStoryWithWorkitemType\" hide-on-click=\"\" class=\"agi-dropdown-menu-custom-item\"><span class=\"workitem-icon\" style=\"background-color: rgb(201, 177, 81);\">ARTQA</span><span>美术验收</span></\n  command=\"createSubStoryWithWorkitemType\" hide-on-click=\"\" class=\"agi-dropdown-menu-custom-item\"><span class=\"workitem-icon\" style=\"background-color: rgb(92, 136, 197);\">CLIENT</span><span>客户端</span></\n  command=\"createSubStoryWithWorkitemType\" hide-on-click=\"\" class=\"agi-drop