{"type":"message","id":"921c26c2","parentId":"f007d533","timestamp":"2026-05-20T09:35:19.801Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01DSYbVBRPcExQpMBpsJ49HG","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"POST captured: https://www.tapd.cn//api/basic/guide/get_user_unfinished_guides\nForm ID: onhref\nForm action: \nSubmitting form via JS...\nPOST captured: https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/stories/add?parent_id=1131253609001037902&workitem_type=CLIENT\nPOST captured: https://www.tapd.cn//api/basic/guide/get_user_unfinished_guides\nAfter URL: https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/stories/add?parent_id=1131253609001037902&workitem_type=CLIENT\n\nAll POST requests:\n  https://www.tapd.cn//api/basic/guide/get_user_unfinished_guides\n    workspace_id=31253609&types%5B%5D=richtext_editor_insert_btn\n  https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/stories/add?parent_id=1131253609001037902&workitem_type=CLIENT\n    undefined\n  https://www.tapd.cn//api/basic/guide/get_user_unfinished_guides\n    workspace_id=31253609&types%5B%5D=richtext_editor_insert_btn\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"fresh-cloud","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"POST captured: https://www.tapd.cn//api/basic/guide/get_user_unfinished_guides\nForm ID: onhref\nForm action: \nSubmitting form via JS...\nPOST captured: https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/stories/add?parent_id=1131253609001037902&workitem_type=CLIENT\nPOST captured: https://www.tapd.cn//api/basic/guide/get_user_unfinished_guides\nAfter URL: https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/stories/add?parent_id=1131253609001037902&workitem_type=CLIENT\n\nAll POST requests:\n  https://www.tapd.cn//api/basic/guide/get_user_unfinished_guides\n    workspace_id=31253609&types%5B%5D=richtext_editor_insert_btn\n  https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/stories/add?parent_id=1131253609001037902&workitem_type=CLIENT\n    undefined\n  https://www.tapd.cn//api/basic/guide/get_user_unfinished_guides\n    workspace_id=31253