{"type":"message","id":"6cd337f3","parentId":"e79199c7","timestamp":"2026-05-20T09:36:16.189Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"找到了！**`StoryOwner`（处理人）是必填字段**！填了标题和版本但没填处理人，所以表单验证失败了，导致无法提交。\n\n同时注意 force click 也没有触发 POST——说明是 jQuery validate 在阻止。\n\n解决方法：创建子需求时，也需要填处理人。按照 SKILL.md 里的配置，客户端[12]的默认处理人是「王亮亮」，策划[14]是「沈嘉琨」，QA[16]是「孙章强」。\n\n更新脚本，加上处理人填写："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_vrtx_01C9tfCNuHBdZAuXKcmX2bdz","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\create_story.mjs","edits":[{"oldText":"    const subItemConfig = {\n      client: [\n        { type: 'CLIENT', name: '客户端' },\n        { type: 'MASTER', name: '策划' },\n        { type: 'QA', name: 'QA验收' },\n      ],\n      server: [\n        { type: 'SERVERS', name: '服务器' },\n        { type: 'MASTER', name: '策划' },\n        { type: 'QA', name: 'QA验收' },\n      ],\n      design: [\n        { type: 'MASTER', name: '策划' },\n        { type: 'QA', name: 'QA验收' },\n      ],\n      ui: [\n        { type: 'UI', name: 'UI' },\n        { type: 'ARTQA', name: 'UI验收' },\n        { type: 'MASTER', name: '策划' },\n        { type: 'QA', name: 'QA验收' },\n      ],\n      motion: [\n        { type: 'ACTION', name: '2D动作' },\n        { type: 'MASTER', name: '策划' },\n        { type: 'QA', name: 'QA验收' },\n      ],\n      audio: [\n        { type: 'AUDIO', name: '音频' },\n        { type: 'MASTER', name: '策划' },\n        { type: 'QA', name: 'QA验收' },\n      ],\n    };","newText":"    const subItemConfig = {\n      client: [\n        { type: 'CLIENT', name: '客户端', owner: '王亮亮' },\n        { type: 'MASTER', name: '策划', owner: '沈嘉琨' },\n        { type: 'QA', name: 'QA验收', owner: '孙章强' },\n      ],\n      server: [\n        { type: 'SERVERS', name: '服务器', owner: '黄佳瑞' },\n        { type: 'MASTER', name: '策划', owner: '沈嘉琨' },\n        { type: 'QA', name: 'QA验收', owner: '孙章强' },\n      ],\n      design: [\n        { type: 'MASTER', name: '策划', owner: '赵乾' },\n        { type: 'QA', name: 'QA验收', owner: '孙章强' },\n      ],\n      ui: [\n        { type: 'UI', name: 'UI', owner: '狄依格' },\n        { type: 'ARTQA', name: 'UI验收', owner: '狄依格' },\n        { type: 'MASTER', name: '策划', owner: '沈嘉琨' },\n        { type: 'QA', name: 'QA验收', owner: '孙章强' },\n      ],\n      motion: [\n        { type: 'ACTION', name: '2D动作', owner: '江林' },\n        { type: 'MASTER', name: '策划', owner: '沈嘉琨' },\n        { type: 'QA', name: 'QA验收', owner: '孙章强' },\n      ],\n      audio: [\n        { type: 'AUDIO', name: '音频', owner: '吴美霞' },\n        { type: 'MASTER', name: '策划', owner: '沈嘉琨' },\n        { type: 'QA', name: 'QA验收', owner: '孙章强' },\n      ],\n    };"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779269754814,"responseId":"chatcmpl-adbaba0f-f08f-4778-b388-92a6bdd00a6f"}}
