{"type":"message","id":"40eba7c6","parentId":"1b113e6d","timestamp":"2026-05-20T09:41:02.563Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"找到了！点击处理逻辑：\n\n```js\n0 < $(\"#parent_workitem_type_require\").length && (0 == $(\"#StoryParentId\").val() || \"\" == $(\"#StoryParentId\").val())\n  ? TFL.tips.showFlash(\"parent_id fields cannot be empty\", \"error\")\n  : $(\"#submit_save_view\")[0].click()\n```\n\n**问题是：`#parent_workitem_type_require` 元素存在，但 `#StoryParentId` 的值是空的！** 所以显示了\"父需求不能为空\"的错误，没有提交表单。\n\n`parent_id` 参数通过 URL 传入，但没有被填入 `#StoryParentId` 隐藏字段。需要手动设置这个字段："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_vrtx_01P6sSBBcj73YZmrSb6NqYb2","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\create_story.mjs","edits":[{"oldText":"          // 填写标题和必填字段\n          const subTitle = `[${item.name}] ${title}`;\n          await page.fill('#StoryName', subTitle);\n          await page.selectOption('#StoryVersion', { label: version }).catch(() => {});\n          await page.waitForTimeout(500);\n\n          // 填写处理人（必填）\n          const ownerInput = page.locator('#StoryOwnerValue').first();","newText":"          // 确保父需求 ID 被写入隐藏字段（否则表单验证失败）\n          await page.evaluate((sid) => {\n            const parentInput = document.getElementById('StoryParentId');\n            if (parentInput) {\n              parentInput.value = sid;\n              parentInput.dispatchEvent(new Event('change', { bubbles: true }));\n            } else {\n              // 创建隐藏字段\n              const input = document.createElement('input');\n              input.type = 'hidden';\n              input.id = 'StoryParentId';\n              input.name = 'data[Story][parent_id]';\n              input.value = sid;\n              document.querySelector('form').appendChild(input);\n            }\n          }, storyId).catch(e => console.warn('  parent_id set failed:', e.message));\n\n          // 填写标题和必填字段\n          const subTitle = `[${item.name}] ${title}`;\n          await page.fill('#StoryName', subTitle);\n          await page.selectOption('#StoryVersion', { label: version }).catch(() => {});\n          await page.waitForTimeout(500);\n\n          // 填写处理人（必填）\n          const ownerInput = page.locator('#StoryOwnerValue').first();"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779270045968,"responseId":"chatcmpl-cdaa2cc9-cbd1-4e91-bc6e-da857dbe5767"}}
