{"type":"message","id":"382c8d45","parentId":"50bc3961","timestamp":"2026-05-20T10:17:25.189Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The issue is that the template is still creating 17 sub-items. The template ID `1131253609001000039` (for sub-stories) has pre-set sub-items configured. Even though I'm using fetch to create the sub-stories, the template still auto-creates 17 sub-items.\n\nThe root cause: The `data[Template][id]` value `1131253609001000039` being sent in the fetch request is triggering TAPD to auto-create 17 preset sub-items for each sub-story created.\n\nSolution: I need to either:\n1. Send an empty template ID in the fetch request for sub-stories\n\n\n2. Or find a template that doesn't have preset sub-items\n\nLooking at the templates being used - the main story uses `1131253609001000010` (系统默认模板1) which has 17 sub-items that I'm clearing, but the sub-stories are using `1131253609001000039` which also appears to have preset items. The fix is to set `data[Template][id]` to an empty string in the fetch call for sub-stories.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"找到问题了——子需求创建时 `data[Template][id]` 传了 `1131253609001000039`，这个模板也带预设子工作项。需要把子需求的模板 ID 也清空。\n\n马上修："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_vrtx_01Lqs4SfibpZSAqZcTpJfzUC","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\create_story.mjs","edits":[{"oldText":"            formData.append('data[Template][id]', '1131253609001000039');","newText":"            formData.append('data[Template][id]', ''); // 清空模板，避免自动创建预设子工作项"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779272232135,"responseId":"chatcmpl-92d9e46b-35bd-4f73-8a84-cd111d5f5b8d"}}
