{"type":"message","id":"2e0be63c","parentId":"e1dfba1a","timestamp":"2026-05-20T10:19:53.169Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user says the sub-items are still wrong - the category is not \"Task\" but \"一对一\" (1v1). So the workitem_type URL parameter is creating sub-items of type \"1v1 story\" instead of \"Task\". \n\nThe issue is likely that the `workitem_type` values I'm using (CLIENT, MASTER, QA) are creating the wrong type of sub-items. The user wants sub-items of type \"Task\" not \"1v1 Conversation\".\n\nLet me think about this. The sub-items should be of workitem_type that corresponds to \"Task\" in TAPD. But from the HTML I scraped earlier, the workitem types were CLIENT, SERVERS, SPECIAL, ORIGINAL, AUDIO, MASTER, PATTERN, ACTION, QA, ARTSTORY, ARTQA. None of these is \"Task\".\n \nWait - maybe the issue is different. The user is saying the sub-items created are categorized as \"一对一\" (1v1) stories, not as \"Task\" type items. The workitem_type parameter I'm using might be creating sub-stories that inherit the parent story's type (1v1 story) rather than creating actual task-type sub-items. I need to figure out what the correct workitem_type value is for creating Task-type sub-items in TAPD. So the real issue is that when creating sub-items through the URL parameter approach, they're inheriting the parent story's category as \"1v1\" instead of being created as Task-type workitems. The HTML from the detail page shows commands like `createSubStoryWithWorkitemType` for custom types like CLIENT, QA, and MASTER, which suggests these should be created as sub-stories with specific workitem types rather than regular tasks. But the user expects them to show as \"Task\" type in the category field, so maybe TAPD's internal representation maps these custom workitem types to Task when displayed.\n\nThe problem is likely in how I'm submitting the form — I'm passing `workitem_type` as a URL parameter, but not including it in the actual POST data. I need to append the workitem type field to the form body so TAPD knows what type of sub-item to create.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了——子需求的类别创建成了「一对一」（继承父需求类型），而不是「Task」类型。问题是 fetch 提交时没有把 `workitem_type` 带进表单 body，只有 URL 里有，服务端没识别到。\n\n来修一下，把 workitem_type 加进 POST body："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_vrtx_013x23cjq5axhSWihvfjwL2J","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\create_story.mjs","offset":195,"limit":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779272366282,"responseId":"chatcmpl-bfaf6af1-ded2-48d8-a565-bee5862759b4"}}
{"type":"message","id":"1b0f363e","parentId":"2e0be63c","timestamp":"2026-05-20T10:19:53.268Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_013x23cjq5axhSWihvfjwL2J","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    if (storyId && storyId !== 'unknown') {\n      // 导航到第一个子需求创建页面，获取 CSRF token\n      const firstSubUrl = `https://www.tapd.cn/${WORKSPACE_ID}/prong/stories/add?parent_id=${storyId}&workitem_type=${subItems[0].type}`;\n      await page.goto(firstSubUrl, { waitUntil: 'networkidle', timeout: 30000 });\n      await page.waitForTimeout(2000);\n      \n      for (let i = 0; i < subItems.length; i++) {\n        const item = subItems[i];\n        console.log(`  ${i + 1}/${subItems.length} Creating sub-item: ${item.name} (${item.type})`);\n        try {\n          // 如果不是第一个，需先导航到对应类型的创建页\n          if (i > 0) {\n            const subUrl = `https://www.tapd.cn/${WORKSPACE_ID}/prong/stories/add?parent_id=${storyId}&workitem_type=${item.type}`;\n            await page.goto(subUrl, { waitUntil: 'networkidle', timeout: 30000 });\n            await page.waitForTimeout(1500);\n          }\n\n          // 获取当前页面的 CSRF token\n          const currentToken = await page.evaluate(() => {\n            const el = document.querySelector('[name=\"data[add_story_token]\"]');\n            return el ? el.value : '';\n          });\n\n          if (!currentToken) {\n            console.warn(`    ⚠️ No token found for ${item.name}, skipping`);\n            continue;\n          }\n\n          // 用 fetch 在页面内部提交（继承 cookie + session）\n          const subTitle = `[${item.name}] ${title}`;\n\n[67 more lines in file. Use offset=225 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1779272393267}}
