{"type":"message","id":"5d1da8c2","parentId":"e5129d6f","timestamp":"2026-05-20T10:21:08.922Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"关键发现：**表单里没有 `workitem_type` 字段！** `workitem_type` 只在 URL query string 里，服务端是从 URL 读取的，不是从 POST body。\n\n所以之前加的 `formData.append('data[Story][workitem_type]', itemType)` 没用。服务端本来就是从 URL `?workitem_type=CLIENT` 读取的。\n\n那 17 个子需求的根本原因还是 **`data[Template][id]` = `1131253609001000039`**。我在 fetch 里已经把它设为空字符串 `''`，但可能服务端收到空字符串后 fallback 到默认模板了。\n\n需要完全**不发送**这个字段，或者找到一个真正没有预设子工作项的模板 ID。让我试试完全不传 `Template[id]`："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_vrtx_01A2udgUiyP1Y6c4e9bc8WAH","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\create_story.mjs","edits":[{"oldText":"            formData.append('data[Template][id]', ''); // 清空模板，避免自动创建预设子工作项","newText":"            // 不传 Template[id]，避免服务端使用模板自动创建预设子工作项\n            // formData.append('data[Template][id]', '');"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779272452997,"responseId":"chatcmpl-67084016-431e-414f-8f6d-542a3048e51d"}}
