{"type":"message","id":"79a2cbbb","parentId":"7f2a2554","timestamp":"2026-05-20T10:22:14.359Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"请主人再确认一下这张：\n\n🔗 https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/stories/view/1131253609001038010\n\n这次不传 `Template[id]`，服务端应该不会套模板。但我有个猜测——问题可能不是子需求自身的模板，而是 **「一对一」类型**是整个工作空间配置的，`workitem_type=CLIENT` 参数没有被正确识别，还是创建成了默认类型。\n\n如果还是有 17 个，能截图给我看看是哪种子需求类型吗？方便我判断是模板预设还是类型选错了。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779272526214,"responseId":"chatcmpl-cf175d7d-2944-4495-ac05-3d20d52a4fc3"}}
{"type":"message","id":"872e5eef","parentId":"79a2cbbb","timestamp":"2026-05-20T10:24:01.875Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[message_id: om_x100b6fecf50c24b0b216c02eea6f026]\nYousan(叶枝君): 还是不对, 换个思路, 读取一下https://www.tapd.cn/tapd_fe/my/work?dialog_preview_id=story_1131253609001037715这个单子的信息, 学习一下把这个作为客户端开单模板"}],"timestamp":1779272641872}}
{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6fecf50c24b0b216c02eea6f026\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yousan(叶枝君)\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-05-20 18:23 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yousan(叶枝君) (ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"name\": \"Yousan(叶枝君)\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"c8c910c9","parentId":"872e5eef","timestamp":"2026-05-20T10:24:01.876Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"23a13879","parentId":"c8c910c9","timestamp":"2026-05-20T10:24:23.734Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me read the story details from that URL to understand the template structure.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好，先把那张正式单的信息读出来。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_vrtx_019ALWTnVtQbPZ4cagy5KwM6","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\inspect_template_story.mjs","content":"import { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\n\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(fileURLToPath(import.meta.url));\nconst WS_DIR = path.resolve(__dirname, '..');\nconst cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(path.join(WS_DIR, 'tapd_cookies_yezhijun.json'), 'utf8'));\n\nconst STORY_ID = '1131253609001037715';\nconst WORKSPACE_ID = '31253609';\n\nconst browser = await chromium.launch({ headless: false, args: ['--no-sandbox'] });\nconst context = await browser.newContext();\nawait context.addCookies(cookies);\nconst page = await context.newPage();\n\n// 先打开详情页（普通 view）\nawait page.goto(`https://www.tapd.cn/${WORKSPACE_ID}/prong/stories/view/${STORY_ID}`, { waitUntil: 'networkidle', timeout: 30000 });\nawait page.waitForTimeout(4000);\n\n// 截图\nawait page.screenshot({ path: path.join(WS_DIR, 'media', 'template_story.png'), fullPage: false });\nconsole.log('Screenshot saved');\n\n// 抓取页面文字内容\nconst bodyText = await page.locator('body').innerText().catch(() => '');\nconsole.log('\\n=== Page text (first 3000 chars) ===');\nconsole.log(bodyText.substring(0, 3000));\n\n// 找子需求列表\nconst subStories = await page.locator('[class*=\"sub-story\"], [class*=\"substory\"], [class*=\"child-story\"]').allTextContents();\nconsole.log('\\n=== Sub story texts ===');\nsubStories.forEach((t, i) => console.log(`[${i}] ${t.trim().substring(0, 200)}`));\n\n// 找\"子需求\"区域的 HTML\nconst html = await page.content();\n// 找子工作项相关\nconst subIdx = html.indexOf('CLIENT');\nif (subIdx > 0) console.log('\\nCLIENT context:', html.substring(subIdx - 200, subIdx + 500));\n\n// 打印页面所有 XHR 请求\nconst xhrs = [];\npage.on('response', async resp => {\n  if (resp.url().includes('tapd.cn') && resp.url().includes('sub')) {\n    const t = await resp.text().catch(() => '');\n    xhrs.push({ url: resp.url(), body: t.substring(0, 300) });\n  }\n});\n\n// 尝试打开 tapd_fe 版本\nawait page.goto(`https://www.tapd.cn/tapd_fe/${WORKSPACE_ID}/story/detail/${STORY_ID}`, { waitUntil: 'networkidle', timeout: 30000 });\nawait page.waitForTimeout(5000);\nawait page.screenshot({ path: path.join(WS_DIR, 'media', 'template_story_fe.png'), fullPage: false });\nconsole.log('FE screenshot saved');\n\n// 抓子工作项数量\nconst countEl = await page.locator('text=/子工作项|子需求/').first().textContent().catch(() => '');\nconsole.log('\\nSub item count text:', countEl);\n\n// 找所有 workitem-icon span\nconst icons = await page.locator('.workitem-icon, [class*=\"workitem-icon\"]').allTextContents();\nconsole.log('\\nWorkitem icons:', icons);\n\n// 找子需求类型列表\nconst subTypes = await page.locator('[class*=\"sub-workitem\"], [class*=\"sub-story-item\"]').allTextContents();\nconsole.log('\\nSub types:', subTypes.slice(0, 20));\n\nawait browser.close();\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779272641877,"responseId":"chatcmpl-5efec3d9-abf7-4475-a58c-d3c98bb0f462"}}
