{"type":"message","id":"4603955d","parentId":"29049bbd","timestamp":"2026-05-20T10:27:00.575Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"太好了！从 XHR 响应拿到了关键数据：\n\n**父需求 `1037715` 的子需求 IDs：**\n`children_id: \"||1131253609001037716|1131253609001037717|1131253609001037718\"`\n\n**模板 ID：** `templated_id: \"1131253609001000047\"`（这是故事模板，不是触发预设的那个）\n\n**关键：** `workitem_type_id: \"1131253609001000049\"`（父需求本身的类型 ID）\n\n现在去查3个子需求（716/717/718）的 `workitem_type_id`，这就是我需要照抄的类型："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_vrtx_01EpgTq6ks81J9VoaBELiQZk","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\get_substory_types.mjs","content":"import fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\n\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(fileURLToPath(import.meta.url));\nconst WS_DIR = path.resolve(__dirname, '..');\nconst cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(path.join(WS_DIR, 'tapd_cookies_yezhijun.json'), 'utf8'));\nconst cookieStr = cookies.map(c => `${c.name}=${c.value}`).join('; ');\n\n// 3 个子需求 ID\nconst subIds = ['1131253609001037716', '1131253609001037717', '1131253609001037718'];\n\nfor (const id of subIds) {\n  const resp = await fetch('https://www.tapd.cn/api/aggregation/workitem_aggregation/common_get_info', {\n    method: 'POST',\n    headers: {\n      'Cookie': cookieStr,\n      'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n      'User-Agent': 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36',\n      'X-Requested-With': 'XMLHttpRequest',\n    },\n    body: JSON.stringify({\n      workspace_id: '31253609',\n      story_id: id,\n    })\n  });\n  const text = await resp.text();\n  \n  // 解析关键字段\n  try {\n    const data = JSON.parse(text);\n    const story = data?.data?.get_info_ret?.data?.Story;\n    if (story) {\n      console.log(`\\nStory ${id}:`);\n      console.log(`  name: ${story.name}`);\n      console.log(`  workitem_type_id: ${story.workitem_type_id}`);\n      console.log(`  owner: ${story.owner}`);\n      console.log(`  status: ${story.status}`);\n      console.log(`  parent_id: ${story.parent_id}`);\n    } else {\n      console.log(`\\nStory ${id}: no data`);\n      console.log('  raw:', text.substring(0, 300));\n    }\n  } catch(e) {\n    console.log(`\\nStory ${id}: parse error`);\n    console.log('  raw:', text.substring(0, 300));\n  }\n}\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779272803184,"responseId":"chatcmpl-c54957a6-41f6-4a66-94b3-dc14790ba127"}}
