{"type":"message","id":"736d7760","parentId":"e1fdf8eb","timestamp":"2026-05-20T10:32:46.925Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user says the story type is wrong, and they've changed it - it should be \"VSMODE\" type. I need to find the workitem_type_id for VSMODE. From the earlier inspection, I saw \"VSMODE\" in the workitem icons list. Let me look at the parent story 1037715 which had workitem_type_id \"1131253609001000049\" - but wait, the user says the main story category should be VSMODE.\n\nI need to find the VSMODE workitem_type_id. Let me check what the user changed - they likely changed the parent story's type to VSMODE. I should look up the VSMODE workitem_type_id from the page data we already captured, or read the current state of story 1038028 to see what type it is now.\n\n\nThe user mentioned they already fixed the parent story's category to VSMODE, so I need to identify what the VSMODE workitem_type_id is from the workitem icons data we have.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好，需要找 VSMODE 类型的 `workitem_type_id`。主人刚改过 `1038028`，直接读它的当前类型："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_vrtx_0166sNV8AuPZxCUE3j4veNVe","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\get_story_typeid.mjs","content":"import { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\n\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(fileURLToPath(import.meta.url));\nconst WS_DIR = path.resolve(__dirname, '..');\nconst cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(path.join(WS_DIR, 'tapd_cookies_yezhijun.json'), 'utf8'));\n\nconst STORY_ID = process.argv[2] || '1131253609001038028';\nconst WORKSPACE_ID = '31253609';\n\nconst browser = await chromium.launch({ headless: false, args: ['--no-sandbox', '--disable-blink-features=AutomationControlled'] });\nconst context = await browser.newContext({\n  userAgent: 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/120.0.0.0 Safari/537.36',\n});\nawait context.addInitScript(() => { Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'webdriver', { get: () => undefined }); window.chrome = { runtime: {} }; });\nawait context.addCookies(cookies);\nconst page = await context.newPage();\n\nconst captured = [];\npage.on('response', async resp => {\n  const url = resp.url();\n  if (url.includes('common_get_info') || url.includes('get_info')) {\n    try {\n      const text = await resp.text();\n      if (text.includes('workitem_type_id')) captured.push(text);\n    } catch(e) {}\n  }\n});\n\nawait page.goto(`https://www.tapd.cn/tapd_fe/${WORKSPACE_ID}/story/detail/${STORY_ID}`, { waitUntil: 'networkidle', timeout: 30000 });\nawait page.waitForTimeout(3000);\n\nfor (const raw of captured) {\n  try {\n    const data = JSON.parse(raw);\n    const story = data?.data?.get_info_ret?.data?.Story || data?.data?.get_workitem_basic_info_ret?.data;\n    if (story && story.id === STORY_ID) {\n      console.log(`name: ${story.name}`);\n      console.log(`workitem_type_id: ${story.workitem_type_id}`);\n      console.log(`owner: ${story.owner}`);\n    }\n  } catch(e) {}\n}\n\nawait browser.close();\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779273143739,"responseId":"chatcmpl-683a27a3-b527-4452-91ea-803279ba2b0f"}}
