{"type":"message","id":"01116c7d","parentId":"eca5db08","timestamp":"2026-05-20T10:35:45.619Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"拿到了！但 **VSMODE 不在这 17 个预设里**。主人说需求类别要是 VSMODE，这是**父需求本身的类型**，不是子需求的类型。\n\n现在问题明确了：\n- **父需求的 `workitem_type_id`** 要用 VSMODE 的 ID（`1131253609001000049` 是什么类型？）\n- **预设 17 个子需求**的根因是模板 `1131253609001000010` 带了预设，服务端在创建时自动触发\n\n让我查一下 `1131253609001000049` 和 `1131253609001000048` 是什么，以及找到 VSMODE 的正确 typeId：\n\n从之前的数据里——模板单 `1037715` 的 `workitem_type_id = 1131253609001000049`，是一个 1V1 需求，页面上显示 `VSMODE` icon。所以 **`1131253609001000049` 就是 VSMODE 类型**！\n\n好，主需求类型已经对了。现在核心问题是：**怎么创建时不触发 17 个预设子工作项**。\n\n从 preset_items 接口知道，这 17 个预设是绑定在模板 `1131253609001000010` 上的。解决方案：**创建时禁用 preset 自动创建**。TAPD 表单里那个提示说「需求提交保存后，系统将自动生成预设内容」，说明这是服务端在创建时触发的。\n\n关键在于：表单里是否有开关来控制 preset 是否执行？看看 form 里有没有跟 preset 相关的字段：\n\n`data[auto_succeed_story_name]` 之前看到了，`= 1`。这个可能跟 preset 有关，试试把它设为 `0`，或者找 `preset` 相关字段："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_vrtx_01JW3nknsjGCkPU6Egyq5VdE","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\inspect_preset_fields.mjs","content":"import { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\n\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(fileURLToPath(import.meta.url));\nconst WS_DIR = path.resolve(__dirname, '..');\nconst cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(path.join(WS_DIR, 'tapd_cookies_yezhijun.json'), 'utf8'));\nconst WORKSPACE_ID = '31253609';\n\nconst browser = await chromium.launch({ headless: false, args: ['--no-sandbox'] });\nconst context = await browser.newContext({ userAgent: 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36' });\nawait context.addCookies(cookies);\nconst page = await context.newPage();\n\n// 监听创建请求，看服务端接受的完整 POST body\npage.on('request', req => {\n  if (req.method() === 'POST' && req.url().includes('stories/add')) {\n    console.log('\\n=== POST stories/add ===');\n    console.log('Body:', req.postData());\n  }\n});\n\nawait page.goto(`https://www.tapd.cn/${WORKSPACE_ID}/prong/stories/add`, { waitUntil: 'networkidle', timeout: 30000 });\nawait page.waitForTimeout(2000);\n\n// 找所有 preset 相关字段\nconst presetFields = await page.evaluate(() => {\n  const allInputs = document.querySelectorAll('input, select, textarea');\n  const result = [];\n  allInputs.forEach(el => {\n    const name = el.name || '';\n    const id = el.id || '';\n    const val = (el.value || '').substring(0, 50);\n    if (name.includes('preset') || name.includes('auto') || name.includes('template') || name.includes('Template')) {\n      result.push({ tag: el.tagName, name, id, value: val });\n    }\n  });\n  return result;\n});\nconsole.log('Preset-related fields:');\npresetFields.forEach(f => console.log(`  ${f.tag} name=\"${f.name}\" id=\"${f.id}\" value=\"${f.value}\"`));\n\n// 看页面 HTML 里 preset 关键词\nconst html = await page.content();\nconst presetIdx = html.indexOf('preset');\nconst autoPresetIdx = html.indexOf('auto_preset');\nconst noPresetIdx = html.indexOf('no_preset');\nconsole.log('\\npreset idx:', presetIdx, presetIdx > 0 ? html.substring(presetIdx - 50, presetIdx + 200) : '');\nconsole.log('auto_preset idx:', autoPresetIdx);\nconsole.log('no_preset idx:', noPresetIdx);\n\n// 找 data[Story][workitem_type_id] 字段\nconst typeIdField = html.indexOf('workitem_type_id');\nconsole.log('\\nworkitem_type_id in form:', typeIdField > 0 ? html.substring(typeIdField - 100, typeIdField + 200) : 'NOT FOUND');\n\nawait browser.close();\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai-proxy","model":"giant-claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779273316212,"responseId":"chatcmpl-cb9f3fbd-35ab-4b4c-bdfb-bd0feaee9e4b"}}
