{"type":"message","id":"0d0d3970","parentId":"86d01d9d","timestamp":"2026-05-20T10:49:26.890Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about the \"当前新学习的技能列表\" - meaning the list of skills I've recently learned/created. They're referring to the skills listed in the `<available_skills>` section, which are the skills installed in the system.\n\nLet me check what skills are available in the OpenClaw system, and specifically mention any recently created/learned skills.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"当前已安装的技能有：\n\n1. **feishu-doc** — 飞书文档读写\n2. **feishu-drive** — 飞书云盘管理\n3. **feishu-perm** — 飞书文档权限\n4. **feishu-wiki** — 飞书知识库导航\n5. **skill-creator** — 创建/编辑/整理技能文件\n6. **taskflow** — 多步骤持久化任务编排\n7. **taskflow-inbox-triage** — 收件箱分流示例\n\n没有新的学习，如果想让我把 TAPD 提单流程做成一个 skill 方便以后复用也可以👍"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":113677,"output":221,"cacheRead":17152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":131050,"cost":{"input":0.01591478,"output":0.00006188000000000001,"cacheRead":0.000480256,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.016456916}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779274160163,"responseId":"26540554-6e31-4b65-a260-371dc2583ce3"}}
