{"type":"message","id":"1eae3ce9","parentId":"cfaa93af","timestamp":"2026-05-20T10:51:22.750Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Actually, the cleanest solution is to keep the main scripts in the workspace and just have the SKILL.md reference them. The skill should be about instructions, not about duplicating scripts. Let me just have the SKILL.md reference the existing workspace scripts.\n\nActually wait, the whole point of creating a skill is to package it. Let me think about this differently.\n\nThe SKILL.md should tell Codex what to do. The scripts can live in the workspace. Let me simplify: the skill creates a mapping between the template names and the PresetItems indexes, and the script itself stays in the workspace where it already works. The skill's value is the knowledge of which indexes map to which sub-item types, and the VSMODE workitem_type_id.\n\nLet me simplify the SKILL.md:","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_IIZ5Y6AvewNeivU2GiCJ5746","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\plugin-skills\\tapd-vsmode-story\\SKILL.md","content":"---\nname: tapd-vsmode-story\ndescription: 在 TAPD 上创建 1V1 VSMODE 类型需求单，通过精确控制预设子工作项（create_task 字段）只创建需要的子需求。  \n  触发词：提需求单、创建需求、开需求单、提1v1需求、vsmode需求。  \n  适用：月圆之夜工作区（31253609），叶枝君账号。\n---\n\n# TAPD VSMODE 需求单创建\n\n## 前置条件\n\n- Cookie 有效：`workspace/tapd_cookies_yezhijun.json`\n- Playwright 已安装（workspace 目录下 `node_modules/playwright`）\n- 从 workspace 目录执行脚本\n\n## VSMODE 需求单模板（6种）\n\n父需求类型固定用 VSMODE（workitem_type_id = `1131253609001000049`）。\n预设子工作项共 17 个（索引 0-16），只把目标索引的 `create_task` 设为 `true`：\n\n| 模板 | 激活索引 | 说明 |\n|------|---------|------|\n| `client` | [12, 14, 16] | 客户端[12] + 策划[14] + QA[16] |\n| `server` | [13, 14, 16] | 服务器 + 策划 + QA |\n| `design` | [14, 16] | 策划 + QA |\n| `ui` | [7, 8, 14, 16] | UI + UI验收 + 策划 + QA |\n| `motion` | [2, 14, 16] | 2D动作 + 策划 + QA |\n| `audio` | [11, 14, 16] | 音频 + 策划 + QA |\n\n## 用法\n\n从 workspace 目录执行 `scripts/create_story.mjs`：\n\n```bash\nnode scripts/create_story.mjs \"需求标题\" <template>\n# 默认 template=client，可选: client/server/design/ui/motion/audio\n```\n\n或者在代码中：\n\n```javascript\nconst { createStory } = await import('./scripts/create_story.mjs');\nawait createStory({ title: '需求标题', template: 'client' });\n```\n\n## 关键参数\n\n| 参数 | 类型 | 默认值 |\n|------|------|--------|\n| title | string | 必填 |\n| template | string | `client` |\n| priority | string | `P2` |\n| module | string | `1V1` |\n| version | string | `【1V1】正式版本V2.0` |\n\n## 核心逻辑（实现参考）\n\n1. 打开创建页，读取 `FormData`（含 17 个 `PresetItems[N]`）\n2. 设置 `data[Story][workitem_type_id] = 1131253609001000049`（VSMODE）\n3. 目标索引的 `PresetItems[N][create_task] = true`，其余 `false`\n4. 用 `fetch` POST 提交表单（避免 JS 验证拦截）\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":131,"output":925,"cacheRead":140544,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":141600,"cost":{"input":0.00001834,"output":0.000259,"cacheRead":0.003935232,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004212572}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779274275006,"responseId":"f2282215-623b-4ea1-9cb0-0ce36b738a1d"}}
