ue`.\n\nSo the workspace script is already correct. Let me just run a quick test to make sure.\n\nActually, the user hasn't confirmed v5 works yet. They just said to use 1037715 as the template. Let me run a new test using the latest script.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好，Skill 已更新。模板单的配置已经写进去了。要不要现在跑一张确认一下效果？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":141,"output":563,"cacheRead":145920,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":146624,"cost":{"input":0.00001974,"output":0.00015764000000000002,"cacheRead":0.00408576,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00426314}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779274557351,"responseId":"c6058912-6269-416e-82fe-7a69f1524741"}}
