{"type":"message","id":"ab844ac3","parentId":"53fa0de1","timestamp":"2026-05-20T10:58:11.660Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying that for the PresetItems that are not activated (create_task=false), their data should NOT be sent in the form data at all - they should be completely removed/omitted. This is different from setting create_task=false. The server might still create them even with create_task=false if they're present in the form data.\n\nActually, re-reading: the user said \"没有激活的预设记得删除\" - meaning the preset items that are not activated should be deleted. So the approach should be:\n\n1. Only include the activated preset items' data in the form data\n2. Remove/delete the non-activated ones entirely\n\nThis makes more sense - don't even send the preset items that shouldn't be created, rather than sending them with create_task=false.\n\nSo I need to update the script: instead of setting `create_task=true/false`, I should REMOVE the unneeded PresetItems entries from the FormData entirely before submitting.\n\nLet me update create_story.mjs.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了——不激活的预设直接删掉，不往表单里传。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_LzOOknJXZfTdu8e0APbZ0484","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\create_story.mjs","offset":85,"limit":35}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":5651,"output":317,"cacheRead":141696,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":147664,"cost":{"input":0.0007911400000000001,"output":0.00008876000000000001,"cacheRead":0.003967488,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004847388}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779274687714,"responseId":"32281d83-83d0-4c48-8455-23a39935003a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"68315793","parentId":"ab844ac3","timestamp":"2026-05-20T10:58:11.760Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_LzOOknJXZfTdu8e0APbZ0484","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    await page.selectOption('#StoryPriority', priority);\n    await page.selectOption('#StoryModule', { label: mod });\n    await page.selectOption('#StoryVersion', { label: version });\n    await page.waitForTimeout(500);\n\n    if (description) {\n      try {\n        const descFrame = page.frameLocator('iframe#StoryDescription_ifr').first();\n        await descFrame.locator('body').fill(description);\n      } catch(e) { console.warn('  Description field not available'); }\n    }\n\n    // 用页面内 fetch 提交，精确控制 PresetItems\n    const result = await page.evaluate(async ({ activeIdxs, wsId, parentTypeId }) => {\n      const form = document.getElementById('FormStory');\n      const fd = new FormData(form);\n\n      // 设置父需求类型为 VSMODE\n      fd.set('data[Story][workitem_type_id]', parentTypeId);\n\n      // 精确控制 PresetItems：只把指定索引的 create_task 设为 true，其余 false\n      // 先找所有 PresetItems 索引\n      const allKeys = Array.from(fd.keys());\n      const idxSet = new Set();\n      for (const k of allKeys) {\n        const m = k.match(/data\\[PresetItems\\]\\[(\\d+)\\]/);\n        if (m) idxSet.add(parseInt(m[1]));\n      }\n      const activeSet = new Set(activeIdxs);\n      for (const idx of idxSet) {\n        fd.set(`data[PresetItems][${idx}][create_task]`, activeSet.has(idx) ? 'true' : 'false');\n      }\n\n      // 设置提交按钮\n      fd.set('data[save_view]', '提交&查看');\n\n[50 more lines in file. Use offset=120 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1779274691760}}
{"type":"message","id":"237595a5","parentId":"68315793","timestamp":"2026-05-20T10:58:18.484Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to change the approach: instead of setting `create_task=false` for inactive items, I need to completely remove all PresetItems entries for inactive indexes from the FormData. But FormData doesn't have a simple `delete` method that works well because each PresetItems entry consists of many fields (id, name, create_task, owner, etc.).\n\nThe best approach: build a new FormData that only includes the activated PresetItems. Let me rewrite the evaluate block.\n\nActually, FormData.delete() does exist - I can just delete all fields related to inactive PresetItems indexes.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_4i521D8zINPM5QDPr4Hw9420","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\create_story.mjs","edits":[{"oldText":"    // 用页面内 fetch 提交，精确控制 PresetItems\n    const result = await page.evaluate(async ({ activeIdxs, wsId, parentTypeId }) => {\n      const form = document.getElementById('FormStory');\n      const fd = new FormData(form);\n\n      // 设置父需求类型为 VSMODE\n      fd.set('data[Story][workitem_type_id]', parentTypeId);\n\n      // 精确控制 PresetItems：只把指定索引的 create_task 设为 true，其余 false\n      // 先找所有 PresetItems 索引\n      const allKeys = Array.from(fd.keys());\n      const idxSet = new Set();\n      for (const k of allKeys) {\n        const m = k.match(/data\\[PresetItems\\]\\[(\\d+)\\]/);\n        if (m) idxSet.add(parseInt(m[1]));\n      }\n      const activeSet = new Set(activeIdxs);\n      for (const idx of idxSet) {\n        fd.set(`data[PresetItems][${idx}][create_task]`, activeSet.has(idx) ? 'true' : 'false');\n      }","newText":"    // 用页面内 fetch 提交，只保留激活的 PresetItems\n    const result = await page.evaluate(async ({ activeIdxs, wsId, parentTypeId }) => {\n      const form = document.getElementById('FormStory');\n      const fd = new FormData(form);\n\n      // 设置父需求类型为 VSMODE\n      fd.set('data[Story][workitem_type_id]', parentTypeId);\n\n      // 删除所有未激活的 PresetItems（完整行数据，不留痕迹）\n      const allKeys = Array.from(fd.keys());\n      const allIdxKeys = {}; // { idx: [key1, key2, ...] }\n      for (const k of allKeys) {\n        const m = k.match(/data\\[PresetItems\\]\\[(\\d+)\\]/);\n        if (m) {\n          const idx = parseInt(m[1]);\n          if (!allIdxKeys[idx]) allIdxKeys[idx] = [];\n          allIdxKeys[idx].push(k);\n        }\n      }\n      const activeSet = new Set(activeIdxs);\n      for (const [idx, keys] of Object.entries(allIdxKeys)) {\n        if (!activeSet.has(parseInt(idx))) {\n          for (const k of keys) fd.delete(k);\n        }\n      }"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":480,"output":798,"cacheRead":147584,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":148862,"cost":{"input":0.00006720000000000001,"output":0.00022344000000000002,"cacheRead":0.004132352,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004422992}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779274691763,"responseId":"a264519f-47c9-42c7-a690-29facb200dc4"}}
