{"type":"message","id":"315503c5","parentId":"9e02869b","timestamp":"2026-05-20T11:01:41.253Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying that the preset sub-items use the wrong owners. The current template (系统默认模板1, ID: 1131253609001000010) has PresetItems with default owners like 王亮亮 for 客户端, 沈嘉琨 for 策划, 孙章强 for QA. But the user wants the actual template story 1037715's owners: 叶枝君 for 客户端, 赵乾A;仲伟国 for 策划, 刘俊鹏;周以天 for QA.\n\nSo I need to:\n1. Find which template has the correct PresetItems owners (the 1V1 preset template)\n2. Or modify the PresetItems owners in the form data before submitting\n\nThe user said \"1v1自己的预设模版\" - maybe there's a secondary template that specifically handles 1V1 stories. Let me check what template ID 1037715 uses - it has `templated_id: 1131253609001000047`. But the PresetItems are from the system template 1131253609001000010.\n\nActually, looking at the PresetItems data again, I noticed that each PresetItem has its own `relate_template_id`. For items 12-15 (客户端, 服务器, 策划, 文案), the `relate_template_id` is `1131253609001000010` (系统默认模板1). But items 0-10 use `1131253609001000039` as their template. And item 16 (QA) uses `1131253609001000040`.\n\nThe user wants the owners to match the template story 1037715. So I need to either:\n1. Use a different template that has the right owners\n2. Or override the owners in the PresetItems form data\n\nThe cleanest way: before submitting, change the owner values in the form data for the activated preset items to match 1037715's actual owners.\n\nLooking at the template 1037715's sub-stories:\n- 客户端 (index 12): owner = 叶枝君\n- 策划 (index 14): owner = 赵乾A;仲伟国\n- QA (index 16): owner = 刘俊鹏;周以天\n\nWhile the current PresetItems defaults are:\n- 客户端: 王亮亮\n- 策划: 沈嘉琨\n- QA: 孙章强\n\nSo I need to override the `owner` field in the PresetItems for the active items before submitting.\n\nActually, wait - maybe the user is talking about a completely different template. Let me check if there are other templates available in TAPD for this workspace. Earlier when I checked, there was only \"系统默认模板1\" visible. But maybe there are more templates in the system.\n\nLet me look at the PresetItems data more carefully. The preset items with index 12 (客户端) and 14 (策划) have `relate_template_id = 1131253609001000010` (系统默认模板1), while index 16 (QA) has `relate_template_id = 1131253609001000040`. This suggests there are multiple templates.\n\nLet me check what the 1V1 preset template is. The user said \"1v1自己的预设模版\" - maybe there's a 1V1-specific template with different owner mappings.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了，需要把激活的预设处理人改成 1v1 模板单里的处理人。先查一下 1v1 的预设模板信息："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_maJbsjoLQt6S1cUBTX764173","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\check_preset_templates.mjs","content":"import { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\n\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(fileURLToPath(import.meta.url));\nconst WS_DIR = path.resolve(__dirname, '..');\nconst cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(path.join(WS_DIR, 'tapd_cookies_yezhijun.json'), 'utf8'));\nconst WORKSPACE_ID = '31253609';\n\nconst browser = await chromium.launch({ headless: true, args: ['--no-sandbox'] });\nconst context = await browser.newContext({\n  userAgent: 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36',\n});\nawait context.addInitScript(() => { Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'webdriver', { get: () => undefined }); });\nawait context.addCookies(cookies);\nconst page = await context.newPage();\nawait page.goto('https://www.tapd.cn', { waitUntil: 'networkidle', timeout: 15000 });\nawait page.waitForTimeout(2000);\n\n// 获取所有可用的 workitem 模板\nconst result = await page.evaluate(async ({ wsId }) => {\n  const r = await fetch(`/api/entity/workitem_template/get_workitem_templates?workspace_id=${wsId}`, {\n    headers: { 'X-Requested-With': 'XMLHttpRequest' }\n  });\n  return r.text();\n}, { wsId: WORKSPACE_ID });\n\ntry {\n  const data = JSON.parse(result);\n  const templates = data?.data || [];\n  console.log('All workitem templates:');\n  (Array.isArray(templates) ? templates : Object.values(templates)).forEach(t => {\n    console.log(`  id=${t.id} name=${t.name} entity_type=${t.entity_type} workspace_id=${t.workspace_id}`);\n  });\n} catch(e) {\n  console.log('raw:', result.substring(0, 500));\n}\n\n// 查1v1预设模板的处理人\n// 已知 客户端[12] relate_template_id = 1131253609001000010\n// 已知 QA[16] relate_template_id = 1131253609001000040\n// 看看这些 template 的 preset_items 分别是什么\nconst templateIdsToCheck = ['1131253609001000010', '1131253609001000040', '1131253609001000039', '1131253609001000047'];\nfor (const tplId of templateIdsToCheck) {\n  const r2 = await page.evaluate(async ({ wsId, tId }) => {\n    const r = await fetch(`/api/entity/workitem_template/get_preset_items?workspace_id=${wsId}&template_id=${tId}`, {\n      headers: { 'X-Requested-With': 'XMLHttpRequest' }\n    });\n    return r.text();\n  }, { wsId: WORKSPACE_ID, tId: tplId });\n\n  try {\n    const data2 = JSON.parse(r2);\n    const items = data2?.data?.preset_items_tree || [];\n    console.log(`\\nTemplate ${tplId} preset items:`);\n    items.forEach(item => {\n      console.log(`  [${item.relate_workitem_type_english_name}] ${item.name} -> owner=${item.owner}`);\n    });\n    if (items.length === 0) console.log('  无预设');\n  } catch(e) {\n    console.log(`\\nTemplate ${tplId}: error`, r2.substring(0, 100));\n  }\n}\n\nawait browser.close();\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":3046,"output":1623,"cacheRead":146432,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":151101,"cost":{"input":0.00042644000000000004,"output":0.00045444,"cacheRead":0.004100096,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004980976}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779274888409,"responseId":"d85e5e24-2906-454