{"type":"message","id":"f571f0b8","parentId":"7b657d9c","timestamp":"2026-05-20T11:02:10.735Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Wait, I don't even need to run a script for this. I already have the data from the inspect_preset_full.mjs run earlier. That showed:\n\nPresetItems for the form (system default template 1131253609001000010):\n- [12] 客户端 owner=王亮亮;, relate_template_id=1131253609001000010\n- [14] 策划 owner=沈嘉琨;, relate_template_id=1131253609001000010\n- [16] QA owner=孙章强;, relate_template_id=1131253609001000040\n\nAnd from the get_preset_items API earlier:\n- [12] 客户端 owner=王亮亮;\n- [14] 策划 owner=沈嘉琨;\n- [16] QA owner=孙章强;\n\nBut the user wants them to match the template story 1037715:\n- 客户端 owner=叶枝君;\n- 策划 owner=赵乾A;仲伟国;\n- QA owner=刘俊鹏;周以天;\n\nSo I need to modify the PresetItems owners in the FormData to match the template story's owners. The simplest approach: in the evaluate block, after deleting inactive PresetItems, override the owner field for the active ones.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"查到了。需要在提交前把激活的预设**处理人**覆盖成模板单 `1037715` 的值："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_FJw0RZcoP12acxUftSdl4237","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\create_story.mjs","edits":[{"oldText":"      // 删除所有未激活的 PresetItems（完整行数据，不留痕迹）\n      const allKeys = Array.from(fd.keys());\n      const allIdxKeys = {}; // { idx: [key1, key2, ...] }\n      for (const k of allKeys) {\n        const m = k.match(/data\\[PresetItems\\]\\[(\\d+)\\]/);\n        if (m) {\n          const idx = parseInt(m[1]);\n          if (!allIdxKeys[idx]) allIdxKeys[idx] = [];\n          allIdxKeys[idx].push(k);\n        }\n      }\n      const activeSet = new Set(activeIdxs);\n      for (const [idx, keys] of Object.entries(allIdxKeys)) {\n        if (!activeSet.has(parseInt(idx))) {\n          for (const k of keys) fd.delete(k);\n        }\n      }","newText":"      // 删除所有未激活的 PresetItems（完整行数据，不留痕迹）\n      const allKeys = Array.from(fd.keys());\n      const allIdxKeys = {};\n      for (const k of allKeys) {\n        const m = k.match(/data\\[PresetItems\\]\\[(\\d+)\\]/);\n        if (m) {\n          const idx = parseInt(m[1]);\n          if (!allIdxKeys[idx]) allIdxKeys[idx] = [];\n          allIdxKeys[idx].push(k);\n        }\n      }\n      const activeSet = new Set(activeIdxs);\n      for (const [idx, keys] of Object.entries(allIdxKeys)) {\n        if (!activeSet.has(parseInt(idx))) {\n          for (const k of keys) fd.delete(k);\n        }\n      }\n\n      // 激活的预设覆盖处理人为模板单 1037715 对应的值\n      // 索引12(客户端)->叶枝君, 索引14(策划)->赵乾A;仲伟国, 索引16(QA)->刘俊鹏;周以天\n      const ownerOverrides = {\n        12: '叶枝君;',\n        14: '赵乾A;仲伟国;',\n        16: '刘俊鹏;周以天;',\n      };\n      for (const idx of activeIdxs) {\n        const override = ownerOverrides[idx];\n        if (override) {\n          fd.set(`data[PresetItems][${idx}][owner]`, override);\n        }\n      }"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":347,"output":963,"cacheRead":151424,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":152734,"cost":{"input":0.000048580000000000006,"output":0.00026964000000000003,"cacheRead":0.0042398719999999996,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004558092}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779274922104,"responseId":"c018b17d-925d-4da2-9e95-a6ccd94db916"}}
