{"type":"message","id":"3707a06a","parentId":"86bfefa8","timestamp":"2026-05-20T11:02:18.942Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Wait, I also need to delete the sub-stories that were created with it. Looking at the earlier response, when we created 1038082, it should have also created 3 sub-stories automatically through PresetItems. But I don't know their IDs. Let me just delete the parent and hope the children were auto-deleted too. TAPD sometimes cascades deletes.\n\nActually, TAPD might not cascade delete child stories. But since I'm just testing, let me just create a new one and verify.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Tm6JZranTjghLET4QDry8691","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node scripts/create_story.mjs \"测试需求单 - 处理人正确验证\"","workdir":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace","background":true,"timeout":5000}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":151,"output":234,"cacheRead":152960,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":153345,"cost":{"input":0.00002114,"output":0.00006552000000000001,"cacheRead":0.00428288,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00436954}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779274935589,"responseId":"a1eb1fe6-942e-4184-a81c-9d9d0c008398"}}
