{"type":"message","id":"6a3a5466","parentId":"9d80d546","timestamp":"2026-05-20T11:07:43.420Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the full picture! The 1v1 template (1131253609001000047) has 13 preset sub-items:\n\n[0] 原画 - type_id 0039 - 邝应桥;阳祯;\n[1] UI - type_id 0028 - 张龙慎;\n[2] UI验收 - type_id 0031 - 张龙慎;\n[3] 动作 - type_id 0047 - 王晓松;\n[4] 特效 - type_id 0038 - 肖和;\n[5] 特效验收 - type_id 0031 - 肖和;\n[6] 音频 - type_id 0041 - 吴美霞;傅一然;温佳音;\n[7] **客户端** - type_id 0033 - **叶枝君** ← 跟1037715一致!\n[8] 服务器 - type_id 0034 - 胡新雷1;\n[9] **策划** - type_id 0043 - **赵乾A;仲伟国** ← 跟1037715一致!\n[10] **QA** - type_id 0032 - **刘俊鹏** ← 注意：这里只有刘俊鹏，没有周以天! (1037715的QA是刘俊鹏;周以天)\n[11] UI动效 - type_id 0038 - 肖和;\n[12] UI动效验收 - type_id 0031 - 肖和;\n\nSo the 1v1 template has 13 items instead of 17, and the owners match 1037715 for client/planning but QA only has 刘俊鹏 (not 刘俊鹏;周以天 like in 1037715).\n\nThe user's instruction is clear:\n1. Replace the 17 system default presets with this 1v1 template's 13 presets\n2. Use the 1v1 template's owners (which already match 1037715)\n\nSo I need to:\n1. Change the SKILL.md to reference these 13 items instead of the old 17\n2. Update the create_story.mjs to use this 1v1 template's preset items\n3. The template indexes need to be recalculated since there are 13 items not 17\n\nNew index mapping for 1v1 template:\n[0] 原画\n[1] UI\n[2] UI验收\n[3] 动作\n[4] 特效\n[5] 特效验收\n[6] 音频\n[7] 客户端\n[8] 服务器\n[9] 策划\n[10] QA\n[11] UI动效\n[12] UI动效验收\n\nClient template activates: [7]客户端, [9]策划, [10]QA\nServer template activates: [8]服务器, [9]策划, [10]QA\nDesign template activates: [9]策划, [10]QA\nUI template activates: [1]UI, [2]UI验收, [9]策划, [10]QA\nMotion template activates: [3]动作, [9]策划, [10]QA\nAudio template activates: [6]音频, [9]策划, [10]QA\n\nAnd importantly - since we're using this template's PresetItems, we can load the template directly. The script should select this template ID (1131253609001000047) instead of clearing it, and then only keep the activated items.\n\nWait - but the current approach is:\n1. Open `prong/stories/add` (uses system default template 1131253609001000010 with 17 items)\n2. Delete inactive PresetItems\n3. Override owners\n\nNew approach should be simpler:\n1. Open the create page WITH the 1v1 template (1131253609001000047)\n2. The form will load with that template's 13 preset items instead of 17\n3. Delete the ones we don't want\n4. Submit\n\nBut we can't change the template dropdown because it's hidden. However, we could:\n- Navigate to `/prong/stories/add?template_id=1131253609001000047` \n- Or use `data[Template][id] = 1131253609001000047` in the form data\n\nWait, actually - looking at the current script, we keep the template at the default (which loads 17 presets) and then manually delete/override. But the better approach is to set the template to 1131253609001000047 first, which would load with only 13 presets with the correct owners already!\n\nBut the issue is that changing TemplateId via JS doesn't trigger loading the new presets (the select element is hidden/disabled). We'd need to trigger the change event properly.\n\nAlternatively, we can just pass `data[Template][id] = 1131253609001000047` in the submitted form data. But the form was already loaded with the default template's fields, so the PresetItems fields in the HTML are already set from the default template.\n\nHmm, the simplest approach:\n1. Set `data[Template][id] = 1131253609001000047` in the form data\n2. Don't include any PresetItems in the form data at all (let the server auto-generate them from the template)\n3. BUT that would create ALL 13 presets, not just the 3 we want\n\nSo we still need the selective approach. Let me think...\n\nOption A: Use default template, manually delete items → we delete 14 of 17\nOption B: Use 1v1 template, manually delete items → we delete 10 of 13\n\nBoth require the same pattern. The difference is the indexes. With option B, the items already have the correct owners (叶枝君, 赵乾A;仲伟国, 刘俊鹏), so we don't need owner overrides!\n\nLet me go with Option B: set the template to 1131253609001000047, and when the form loads, it'll have 13 presets. Then delete the ones we don't want.\n\nBut wait - the form loads with the default template's presets in its HTML. If we just change `data[Template][id]` in the formdata without actually loading the template's presets via the page, the PresetItems fields in the FormData will still be from the default template.\n\nI think the correct approach is:\n1. Set `data[Template][id] = 1131253609001000047` \n2. ALSO delete all existing PresetItems from FormData\n3. The server will then auto-create presets from the 1v1 template... but it would create ALL 13\n\nThat won't work either because we only want 3.\n\nOK so the approach should be: load the page normally (default template), then just pass the correct data through. The server processes whatever PresetItems we include. If we set the template to 1131253609001000047 and only include the 3 items we want with their owners from that template, it should work.\n\nLet me simplify: just use the workspaces approach where I:\n1. Set template ID to 1131253609001000047\n2. Delete all existing PresetItems from FormData\n3. Rebuild only the 3 we need, with the correct data (type_id, owner, name, etc.)\n\nWait, that's overly complex. Let me just update the index mapping and keep the current approach. The main change is:\n- New indexes (0-12 for 1v1 template) instead of (0-16 for default template)\n- QA owner changed from 孙章强 to 刘俊鹏 (in the PresetItems default)\n- Client owner already matches: 叶枝君\n- 策划 owner already matches: 赵乾A;仲伟国\n\nActually, the simplest approach: since the 1v1 template already has the right owners for client/策划/QA, just load the 1v1 template! \n\nThe problem is: how do we tell TAPD to use the 1v1 template instead of the system default? By setting `data[Template][id] = 1131253609001000047` in the submitted form data. But the form was loaded with default template's PresetItems in the HTML...\n\nActually, I think we need to NOT send the PresetItems at all and instead just set the template ID. The server should then use that template to auto-create the presets. BUT that would create all 13, not 3.\n\nAlternatively, the most reliable approach: \n1. Load the page normally\n2. Collect the full FormData\n3. Set template ID to 1131253609001000047\n4. Remove ALL PresetItems \n5. Manually add only the 3 PresetItems we need with correct values (type_id, owner, name, create_task=true)\n6. Submit\n\nLet me just do this properly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"找到了！1v1 模板有 **13 个预设子工作项**，处理人已经和我之前覆盖的值一致！\n\n更新脚本——改用 1v1 模板（`1131253609001000047`），只保留需要的 3 项："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_TjzV0RN8BCMu4jcpyQOV3578","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\create_story.mjs","edits":[{"oldText":"// 父需求 workitem_type_id（VSMODE 类型，从模板单 1037715 学到的）\nconst PARENT_WORKITEM_TYPE_ID = '1131253609001000049';","newText":"// 父需求 workitem_type_id（VSMODE）\nconst PARENT_WORKITEM_TYPE_ID = '1131253609001000049';\n\n// 1v1 模板 ID（比系统默认少 4 项，处理人已正确）\nconst ONE_V1_TEMPLATE_ID = '1131253609001000047';"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":766,"output":2187,"cacheRead":161536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":164489,"cost":{"input":0.00010724000000000001,"output":0.00061236,"cacheRead":0.004523008,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005242608}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779275244329,"responseId":"d22fd1c1-695e-4a60-aa4c-de01fd2393eb"}}
