{"type":"message","id":"028dbac5","parentId":"cf93c891","timestamp":"2026-05-20T11:08:07.076Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now update the evaluate block to:\n1. Set template ID to the 1v1 template \n2. Delete ALL existing PresetItems (since they're from the default template)\n3. Re-add only the activated ones with data from the 1v1 template\n4. Remove the owner override since 1v1 template already has correct owners actually...\n\nWait, but the form is loaded with the default template's PresetItems. I can't just load the 1v1 template's PresetItems from the HTML. Let me think about this differently.\n\nThe simplest approach:\n1. Set `data[Template][id] = 1131253609001000047`\n2. Delete ALL existing PresetItems from FormData  \n3. Don't add any PresetItems - let the server handle it with the template\n\nBUT - this would create ALL 13 items, not just 3.\n\nAlternative: \n1. Set `data[Template][id] = 1131253609001000047`\n2. Delete ALL existing PresetItems \n3. Manually reconstruct only the 3 we want\n\nActually, the cleanest approach is what we already have working but with updated indexes and without owner overrides (since the 1v1 template already has correct owners). But the PresetItems loaded into the form are from the default template, not the 1v1 template. So the data for each item (name, type_id, owner) is from the default template.\n\nThe real fix: load the PRESET ITEMS data from the 1v1 template API in the evaluate block and use that to build the correct PresetItems.\n\nHmm, this is getting complex. Let me take a step back.\n\nThe simplest practical approach that works:\n1. Keep loading the page normally (default template)\n2. Change `data[Template][id]` to 1131253609001000047 in the form data\n3. Delete all PresetItems from the FormData\n4. DON'T send any PresetItems at all\n5. The server creates the story with template 1131253609001000047, which will auto-create ALL 13 presets\n\nBut we only want 3...\n\nOK, another approach: Just keep what we have (which works for client template), but update:\n- The indexes to match 1v1 template (but the form is loaded with default template's 17 items, so indexes won't match!)\n- OR: Remove all PresetItems, and the server will use the template. Then delete the unwanted sub-stories after creation.\n\nThis is getting circular. Let me just take the approach that works:\n\n1. The form loads with default template → 17 PresetItems\n2. Set `data[Template][id] = 1131253609001000047`\n3. Delete ALL 17 PresetItems from FormData\n4. The story gets created with template 1131253609001000047 → server auto-creates 13 presets\n5. Then delete the 10 unwanted sub-stories\n\nBut this is worse because now we need to delete 10 instead of controlling it upfront.\n\nActually, wait. Let me re-read the user's request more carefully. They said:\n\n\"清理一下17个子工作项, 读取一下1v1开单模板里面的子工作项\"\n\nClean up the 17 sub-workitems, read the 1v1 template's sub-workitems.\n\nSo the user wants to:\n1. Clean up the 17 default preset items (remove them)\n2. Instead use the 1v1 template's 13 preset items\n3. From those 13, activate only the ones for the client template\n\nSince the 1v1 template has the correct owners, I can use a different strategy:\n1. Set template to 1v1 in the form data\n2. Delete all PresetItems from FormData (since they're from default template)\n3. Rebuild only the 3 PresetItems we need, fetching their data from the 1v1 template\n\nLet me write this properly. I'll fetch the 1v1 template's preset items first, then reconstruct.\n\nActually, the simplest approach: I'll have the evaluate function also fetch the 1v1 template's preset items via API, then only include the ones we want.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"现在更新提交逻辑——改用 1v1 模板的预设："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_0JMpfzsIWCVHTYgpa9om0427","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\create_story.mjs","edits":[{"oldText":"    // 用页面内 fetch 提交，只保留激活的 PresetItems\n    const result = await page.evaluate(async ({ activeIdxs, wsId, parentTypeId }) => {\n      const form = document.getElementById('FormStory');\n      const fd = new FormData(form);\n\n      // 设置父需求类型为 VSMODE\n      fd.set('data[Story][workitem_type_id]', parentTypeId);\n\n      // 删除所有未激活的 PresetItems（完整行数据，不留痕迹）\n      const allKeys = Array.from(fd.keys());\n      const allIdxKeys = {};\n      for (const k of allKeys) {\n        const m = k.match(/data\\[PresetItems\\]\\[(\\d+)\\]/);\n        if (m) {\n          const idx = parseInt(m[1]);\n          if (!allIdxKeys[idx]) allIdxKeys[idx] = [];\n          allIdxKeys[idx].push(k);\n        }\n      }\n      const activeSet = new Set(activeIdxs);\n      for (const [idx, keys] of Object.entries(allIdxKeys)) {\n        if (!activeSet.has(parseInt(idx))) {\n          for (const k of keys) fd.delete(k);\n        }\n      }\n\n      // 激活的预设覆盖处理人为模板单 1037715 对应的值\n      // 索引12(客户端)->叶枝君, 索引14(策划)->赵乾A;仲伟国, 索引16(QA)->刘俊鹏;周以天\n      const ownerOverrides = {\n        12: '叶枝君;',\n        14: '赵乾A;仲伟国;',\n        16: '刘俊鹏;周以天;',\n      };\n      for (const idx of activeIdxs) {\n        const override = ownerOverrides[idx];\n        if (override) {\n          fd.set(`data[PresetItems][${idx}][owner]`, override);\n        }\n      }","newText":"    // 先获取 1v1 模板的预设数据\n    const v1Template = await page.evaluate(async ({ wsId, tplId }) => {\n      const r = await fetch('/api/entity/workitem_template/get_preset_items?workspace_id=' + wsId + '&template_id=' + tplId, {\n        headers: { 'X-Requested-With': 'XMLHttpRequest' }\n      });\n      const data = JSON.parse(await r.text());\n      const items = data?.data?.preset_items_tree || [];\n      return items.map(item => ({\n        id: item.id,\n        name: item.name,\n        type_id: item.relate_workitem_type_id,\n        template_id: item.relate_template_id,\n        owner: item.owner,\n        english_name: item.relate_workitem_type_english_name,\n        color: item.relate_workitem_type_color,\n        preset_relations: JSON.stringify(item.preset_relations || []),\n      }));\n    }, { wsId: WORKSPACE_ID, tplId: ONE_V1_TEMPLATE_ID });\n\n    console.log(`  Loaded ${v1Template.length} preset items from 1v1 template`);\n\n    // 用页面内 fetch 提交，只保留激活的 PresetItems\n    const result = await page.evaluate(async ({ activeIdxs, tplItems, wsId, parentTypeId, tplId }) => {\n      const form = document.getElementById('FormStory');\n      const fd = new FormData(form);\n\n      // 设置父需求类型为 VSMODE，使用 1v1 模板\n      fd.set('data[Story][workitem_type_id]', parentTypeId);\n      fd.set('data[Template][id]', tplId);\n\n      // 删除默认模板带来的所有 PresetItems\n      // FormData 没有遍历+删除的好方法，先收集再删\n      const delKeys = Array.from(fd.keys()).filter(k => k.startsWith('data[PresetItems]'));\n      for (const k of delKeys) fd.delete(k);\n\n      // 只添加激活的 PresetItems，数据来自 1v1 模板\n      const activeSet = new Set(activeIdxs);\n      for (let i = 0; i < tplItems.length; i++) {\n        if (!activeSet.has(i)) continue;\n        const item = tplItems[i];\n        const prefix = `data[PresetItems][${i}]`;\n        fd.append(prefix + '[id]', item.id);\n        fd.append(prefix + '[name]', item.name);\n        fd.append(prefix + '[relate_workitem_type_id]', item.type_id);\n        fd.append(prefix + '[relate_template_id]', item.template_id);\n        fd.append(prefix + '[relation_type]', 'story');\n        fd.append(prefix + '[owner]', item.owner);\n        fd.append(prefix + '[step]', '');\n        fd.append(prefix + '[no_permission]', '0');\n        fd.append(prefix + '[no_permission_tip]', '');\n        fd.append(prefix + '[relate_workitem_type_english_name]', item.english_name);\n        fd.append(prefix + '[relate_workitem_type_color]', item.color);\n        fd.append(prefix + '[preset_relations]', item.preset_relations || '');\n        fd.append(prefix + '[path]', `${i}::`);\n        fd.append(prefix + '[identifier]', item.id);\n        fd.append(prefix + '[create_task]', 'true');\n        fd.append(prefix + '[can_create]', 'true');\n        fd.append(prefix + '[cant_create_reason]', '');\n      }"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":129,"output":2363,"cacheRead":165248,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":167740,"cost":{"input":0.00001806,"output":0.00066164,"cacheRead":0.004626944,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005306644}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779275269250,"responseId":"923d14ae-a36d-4dd0-8a8a-05d4cbea6b39"}}
