{"type":"message","id":"23699b70","parentId":"9462d6db","timestamp":"2026-05-20T12:09:50.799Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants the QA handler to also include 周以天. From the 1v1 template, QA currently has owner=刘俊鹏. Need to change it to 刘俊鹏;周以天.\n\nI need to update:\n1. The create_story.mjs script - the owner override for QA index [10]\n2. The SKILL.md\n3. MEMORY.md\n\nLet me check the current code. The script doesn't have explicit owner overrides anymore - it uses the 1v1 template's preset items as-is. So I need to add a post-processing step to append 周以天 to QA's owner.\n\nLooking at the code, the PresetItems data comes from the API response. I need to modify the owner in the v1Template array before passing it to the evaluate function.\n\nLet me read the relevant part.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_U4jDjVncddnCq5Rj3gYi3100","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\create_story.mjs","edits":[{"oldText":"    console.log(`  Loaded ${v1Template.length} preset items from 1v1 template`);\n\n    // 用页面内 fetch 提交","newText":"    console.log(`  Loaded ${v1Template.length} preset items from 1v1 template`);\n\n    // QA 处理人追加周以天（兵王）\n    const qaItem = v1Template[10];\n    if (qaItem && qaItem.english_name === 'QA') {\n      if (!qaItem.owner.includes('周以天')) {\n        qaItem.owner = (qaItem.owner || '').replace(/;$/, '') + ';周以天;';\n        console.log('  QA owner updated to:', qaItem.owner);\n      }\n    }\n\n    // 用页面内 fetch 提交"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":174590,"output":458,"cacheRead":10112,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":185160,"cost":{"input":0.024442600000000002,"output":0.00012824,"cacheRead":0.00028313599999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.024853976000000003}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779278978915,"responseId":"c80d7b37-1fd2-4314-8523-0eeb2d8