{"type":"message","id":"e9c892fb","parentId":"03a92067","timestamp":"2026-05-20T12:25:57.140Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user specified \"给周以天和西奥开一个需求单\" - meaning the handler should have both 周以天 and 西奥(陈霄豪). But I only set it to 周以天. Let me note this for future - if user says \"给XX和YY开单\", the handler should include both names.\n\nAlso, the description wasn't passed via CLI. Let me update that.\n\nFor now, let me just clean up and confirm.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"测完了 ✅ 指定人开单功能正常。\n\n不过你说了「给周以天和西奥」，母单处理人应该同时包含两人是吧？下次说「给XX和YY开需求单」我就把两人都设进处理人。描述内容的 CLI 支持我补一下："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_UXXb9FQ4HTTls5XLgE5p3827","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\create_story.mjs","edits":[{"oldText":"  const title = process.argv[2] || '测试需求单 - 请忽略';\n  const template = process.argv[3] || 'client';\n  // 第四个参数指定母单处理人（可选）\n  const handler = process.argv[4] || '';\n  createStory({ title, template, handler })","newText":"  const title = process.argv[2] || '测试需求单 - 请忽略';\n  const template = process.argv[3] || 'client';\n  const handler = process.argv[4] || '';\n  const description = process.argv[5] || '';\n  createStory({ title, template, handler, description })"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":77,"output":399,"cacheRead":188800,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":189276,"cost":{"input":0.00001078,"output":0.00011172000000000001,"cacheRead":0.0052864,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0054089}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779279952668,"responseId":"edd27ffb-59d7-4b38-8d1d-3757edf590da"}}
