{"type":"message","id":"4b3c7528","parentId":"6720e591","timestamp":"2026-05-20T12:37:31.892Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user showed an example of the format they want. It's a Feishu-styled hyperlink where the title text itself is a clickable link. In Feishu, the link appears as blue clickable text.\n\nLooking at the message, the format they used is:\n```\n[【0528】周版本 CCG新增线上测试环境用于赛季测试](https://www.tapd.cn/tapd_fe/31253609/story/detail/1131253609001036852)\n```\n\nBut this is the standard markdown link format `[text](url)`. The user said my previous use of this same format was wrong though...\n\nWait - looking more carefully at the conversation history. The user said \"反馈不对, 反馈应该是需求单的标题, 这个标题带上超链接\". Maybe what they meant was:\n\n1. My previous feedback had extra content like \"母单处理人：叶枝君 · 子需求：客户端 + 策划 + QA\" which they didn't want\n2. They just want the title itself as a hyperlink, nothing else\n\nOr maybe in the Feishu context, the user sent this message and the `[text](url)` format rendered correctly on their end as a clickable link. The user is demonstrating that this IS the correct format.\n\nSo the correct feedback should be just the title as a clickable link:\n[标题](链接)\n\nWithout any extra text like \"📋 需求单：\" or \"母单处理人：...\" prefix.\n\nBut then they also want to see the handler and sub-items info... or maybe not?\n\nLet me re-read: \"反馈不对, 反馈应该是需求单的标题, 这个标题带上超链接\"\n\n\"反馈应该是需求单的标题\" - the feedback should BE the title of the story\n\"这个标题带上超链接\" - and this title should be a hyperlink\n\nSo the feedback should be JUST:\n[需求标题](url)\n\nNothing else. Let me update the script output to be just this.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了！反馈格式就是标题本身作为超链接，没有额外前缀。更新脚本："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_xT1kEB16lIEUBDJAPsih6715","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\create_story.mjs","edits":[{"oldText":"    console.log(`3/3 Done!`);\n  