{"type":"message","id":"9b093797","parentId":"f49699ac","timestamp":"2026-05-20T12:49:04.139Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying that when they need to add a sub-story to an existing story, they don't want to use the sub-story template mechanism (which creates all preset items). They just want to add a single sub-story directly.\n\nCurrently the create_story.mjs only creates a whole story with sub-items via PresetItems. The user wants a separate functionality to add a single sub-story to an existing parent story.\n\nI need to:\n1. Create a new script or extend the existing one to support adding a single sub-story to an existing parent story\n2. The sub-story should use the 1v1 workitem_type_id directly (CLIENT 0033, SERVERS 0034, MASTER 0043, QA 0032, etc.)\n3. No nested template/preset items - just create one simple sub-story\n\nLet me think about the simplest implementation. When adding a sub-story to an existing story:\n1. Navigate to the sub-story creation page with parent_id\n2. Set the workitem_type_id\n3. Fill title and handler\n4. Submit with no PresetItems at all\n\nThe URL format is: `https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/stories/add?parent_id=STORY_ID&workitem_type=CLIENT`\n\nFor the workitem_type_id mapping:\n- 客户端: 1131253609001000033\n- 服务器: 1131253609001000034\n- 策划: 1131253609001000043\n- QA: 1131253609001000032\n- UI: 1131253609001000028\n- UI验收: 1131253609001000031\n- etc.\n\nLet me create a simple script `add_sub_story.mjs` that:\n1. Takes a parent story ID, work item name (客户端/服务器/策划/QA/etc.), title, handler\n2. Opens the sub-story creation page\n3. Fills in the fields\n4. Submits with no preset items (delete all PresetItems from FormData)\n5. Returns the URL\n\nLet me implement this.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"明白，给已有需求单独加一个子需求，不套模板。我来实现："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_13UIjBiq2sgTKPLmL3yw3981","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\add_sub_story.mjs","content":"/**\n * 给已有的需求单添加单一子需求（不嵌套模板，不加预设子工作项）\n * \n * 用法: node scripts/add_sub_story.mjs <parent_id> <子需求类型> <标题> [处理人]\n * 示例: node scripts/add_sub_story.mjs 1131253609001037715 服���端 \"新增登录接口\" \"胡新雷1\"\n */\n\nimport { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\n\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(fileURLToPath(import.meta.url));\nconst WS_DIR = path.resolve(__dirname, '..');\nconst COOKIES_FILE = path.join(WS_DIR, 'tapd_cookies_yezhijun.json');\nconst WORKSPACE_ID = '31253609';\n\n// 子需求类型映射（名称 → workitem_type_id 和默认处理人）\nconst SUB_ITEM_TYPES = {\n  '客户端':   { typeId: '1131253609001000033', owner: '叶枝君' },\n  '服务器':   { typeId: '1131253609001000034', owner: '胡新雷1' },\n  '策划':     { typeId: '1131253609001000043', owner: '赵乾A;仲伟国' },\n  'QA':      { typeId: '1131253609001000032', owner: '刘俊鹏;周以天' },\n  'UI':      { typeId: '1131253609001000028', owner: '张龙慎' },\n  'UI验收':   { typeId: '1131253609001000031', owner: '张龙慎' },\n  '动作':     { typeId: '1131253609001000047', owner: '王晓松' },\n  '特效':     { typeId: '1131253609001000038', owner: '肖和' },\n  '特效验收':  { typeId: '1131253609001000031', owner: '肖和' },\n  '音频':     { typeId: '1131253609001000041', owner: '吴美霞;傅一然;温佳音' },\n  '原画':     { typeId: '1131253609001000039', owner: '邝应桥;阳祯' },\n};\n\n// CLI 入口\nconst parentId = process.argv[2];\nconst subType = process.argv[3];\nconst title = process.argv[4];\nconst customOwner = process.argv[5] || '';\n\nif (!parentId || !subType || !title) {\n  console.error('用法: node scripts/add_sub_story.mjs <parent_id> <子需求类型> <标题> [处理人]');\n  console.error('子需求类型: 客户端 / 服务器 / 策划 / QA / UI / UI验收 / 动作 / 特效 / 音频 / 原画');\n  process.exit(1);\n}\n\nconst type = SUB_ITEM_TYPES[subType];\nif (!type) {\n  console.error(`未知子需求类型: ${subType}`);\n  console.error(`可用: ${Object.keys(SUB_ITEM_TYPES).join(', ')}`);\n  process.exit(1);\n}\n\nconst owner = customOwner || type.owner;\nconst ENGLISH_NAMES = {\n  '1131253609001000033': 'Client',\n  '1131253609001000034': 'Servers',\n  '1131253609001000043': 'Master',\n  '1131253609001000032': 'QA',\n  '1131253609001000028': 'ArtStory',\n  '1131253609001000031': 'ArtQA',\n  '1131253609001000047': 'Action',\n  '1131253609001000038': 'Special',\n  '1131253609001000041': 'Audio',\n  '1131253609001000039': 'Original',\n};\n\nasync function addSubStory() {\n  const cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(COOKIES_FILE, 'utf8'));\n\n  const browser = await chromium.launch({\n    headless: false,\n    args: ['--no-sandbox', '--disable-blink-features=AutomationControlled'],\n  });\n  const context = await browser.newContext({\n    userAgent: 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36',\n  });\n  await context.addInitScript(`\n    Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'webdriver', { get: () => undefined });\n    Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'plugins', { get: () => [1, 2, 3, 4, 5] });\n  `);\n  await context.addCookies(cookies);\n  const page = await context.newPage();\n\n  try {\n    // 打开子需求创建页面\n    const englishName = ENGLISH_NAMES[type.typeId] || 'CLIENT';\n    const addUrl = `https://www.tapd.cn/${WORKSPACE_ID}/prong/stories/add?parent_id=${parentId}&workitem_type=${englishName}`;\n    console.log(`1/2 Opening sub-story create page...`);\n    await page.goto(addUrl, { waitUntil: 'networkidle', timeout: 30000 });\n    if (page.url().includes('login')) throw new Error('TAPD session expired');\n    await page.waitForTimeout(2000);\n\n    // 获取 CSRF token\n    const token = await page.evaluate(() => {\n      const el = document.querySelector('[name=\"data[add_story_token]\"]');\n      return el ? el.value : '';\n    });\n    if (!token) throw new Error('CSRF token not found');\n\n    // 用 fetch 提交，清除所有 PresetItems（不嵌套模板）\n    const result = await page.evaluate(async ({ sid, wsId, typeId, subTitle, subOwner, tok }) => {\n      const form = document.getElementById('FormStory');\n      const fd = new FormData(form);\n\n      // 设置必填字段\n      fd.set('data[add_story_token]', tok);\n      fd.set('data[Story][name]', subTitle);\n      fd.set('data[Story][parent_id]', sid);\n      fd.set('data[Story][workitem_type_id]', typeId);\n      fd.set('data[Story][priority]', 'P2');\n      fd.set('data[Story][module]', '1V1');\n      fd.set('data[Story][version]', '【1V1】正式版本V2.0');\n      fd.set('data[Story][owner]', subOwner);\n\n      // 删除所有 PresetItems（不加预设子工作项）\n      const keysToDelete = Array.from(fd.keys()).filter(k => k.startsWith('data[PresetItems]'));\n      for (const k of keysToDelete) fd.delete(k);\n\n      // 不设置模板\n      fd.set('data[Template][id]', '');\n\n      fd.set('data[save_view]', '提交&查看');\n\n      const resp = await fetch(`/${wsId}/prong/stories/add?parent_id=${sid}&workitem_type=CLIENT`, {\n        method: 'POST',\n        body: fd,\n        redirect: 'follow',\n      });\n      const text = await resp.text();\n      const idMatch = text.match(/\\\"id\\\":\\\"(1131253609\\d+)\\\"/);\n      return {\n        status: resp.status,\n        finalUrl: resp.url,\n        subId: idMatch ? idMatch[1] : null,\n      };\n    }, {\n      sid: parentId,\n      wsId: WORKSPACE_ID,\n      typeId: type.typeId,\n      subTitle: title,\n      subOwner: owner,\n      tok: token,\n    });\n\n    if (result.status !== 200) throw new Error(`Submit failed: ${result.status}`);\n\n    const subUrl = result.subId\n      ? `https://www.tapd.cn/${WORKSPACE_ID}/prong/stories/view/${result.subId}`\n      : result.finalUrl;\n\n    console.log(`2/2 Done!`);\n    console.log(`\\n[${title}](${subUrl})`);\n    return { url: subUrl, subId: result.subId };\n\n  } finally {\n    await browser.close();\n  }\n}\n\naddSubStory()\n  .then(r => { console.log('SUCCESS:', JSON.stringify(r)); process.exit(0); })\n  .catch(e => { console.error('FAILED:', e.message); process.exit(1); });\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":5766,"output":2407,"cacheRead":196608,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":204781,"cost":{"input":0.0008072400000000001,"output":0.00067396,"cacheRead":0.005505024,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.006986224}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779281327304,"responseId":"10637473-88d7-4c52-95e5-31054bb773e7"}}
