{"type":"message","id":"bb09b09c","parentId":"85ee0d10","timestamp":"2026-05-20T12:57:12.885Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to learn how to manage Git permissions on their GitLab instance at git.devcloud.ztgame.com. They've provided the cookies to authenticate. I need to:\n\n1. Save the cookie to a file\n2. Use it to access the GitLab API/UI\n3. Figure out how to manage permissions (probably project member management, access levels, etc.)\n\nLet me first save the cookie, then explore the GitLab instance to understand the permission management interface.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"收到，先保存 cookie 然后探索一下 git 平台。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_vKM6bjSfh8JfOT8bM6eB3788","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\gitlab_cookies.json","content":"[\n {\n \"domain\": \"git.devcloud.ztgame.com\",\n \"hostOnly\": true,\n \"httpOnly\": true,\n \"name\": \"_gitlab_session\",\n \"path\": \"/\",\n \"sameSite\": \"no_restriction\",\n \"secure\": true,\n \"session\": true,\n \"storeId\": null,\n \"value\": \"f2181f584a05348a6a8f39437b2e5cf2\"\n },\n {\n \"domain\": \"git.devcloud.ztgame.com\",\n \"hostOnly\": true,\n \"httpOnly\": false,\n \"name\": \"preferred_language\",\n \"path\": \"/\",\n \"sameSite\": \"no_restriction\",\n \"secure\": true,\n \"session\": true,\n \"storeId\": null,\n \"value\": \"en\"\n },\n {\n \"domain\": \"git.devcloud.ztgame.com\",\n \"expirationDate\": 1780397846.210373,\n \"hostOnly\": true,\n \"httpOnly\": true,\n \"name\": \"known_sign_in\",\n \"path\": \"/\",\n \"sameSite\": \"no_restriction\",\n \"secure\": true,\n \"session\": false,\n \"storeId\": null,\n \"value\": \"K2lvbm1FNkhKY04yb3N5cE9rTGJuYnpTa0Zab0VTV0lRWlhidVZxRGhpOGRXa1MzZFdMMEdGczBhQ2xtQmxNU1RLbTFYd3FnaXRGNGZZQ3VTNWl4UjhBNFF6VVlvVVlYL3ZYYlVENkpjVnhtNEJhRnhxaDhmZTNPUzYwdjVLOVUtLUo1SEpOQktXb2hhRnV2S0lFamNKV2c9PQ%3D%3D--fd0f8da49198afd14df0b34a8b36d4d21