ocation\":\"\",\"public_email\":null,\"skype\":\"\",\"linkedin\":\"\",\"twitter\":\"\",\"discord\":\"\",\"website_url\"\n\nMy projects:\n  id=2934 config (yyzy_proj/jiuguan/config) visibility=private\n  id=2751 NightofFullMoon (yyzy/develop_client/nightoffullmoon) visibility=private\n  id=5058 config (yyzy_proj/1v1/config) visibility=private\n  id=4321 cdn_240401 (yyzy_proj/jiuguan/cdn_240401) visibility=private\n  id=4710 gameconfig (yyzy_proj/gordian/gameconfig) visibility=private\n  id=5145 battle1v1 (yyzy_proj/1v1/battle1v1) visibility=private\n  id=2933 proto (yyzy_proj/jiuguan/proto) visibility=private\n  id=5060 proto (yyzy_proj/1v1/proto) visibility=private\n  id=5048 DidaFramework (yyzy_proj/framework/DidaFramework) visibility=private\n  id=5591 20251015cnd (yyzy_proj/backpack/20251015cnd) visibility=private\n","name":"node scripts/inspect_gitlab.mjs"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1779281893492}}
{"type":"message","id":"2a817f9c","parentId":"749ad0b8","timestamp":"2026-05-20T12:58:23.527Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK! I can see the GitLab is accessible. The user is 叶枝君 (username: yezhijun). I can see the projects and their permissions. \n\nNow the user wants to \"管理git权限\" - manage git permissions. In GitLab, this usually means:\n1. Adding/removing members to projects\n2. Changing member roles (Guest, Reporter, Developer, Maintainer, Owner)\n3. Managing group members\n\nLet me explore the member management flow. Looking at the projects:\n- yyzy_proj/1v1/config - Maintainer access\n- yyzy_proj/1v1/battle1v1 - Reporter access\n- yyzy_proj/jiuguan/cdn_240401 - Developer access\n- etc.\n\nFor permission management, I need to:\n1. Know which project to manage\n2. Know who to add/remove and what role\n\nLet me check the member management page for one of the projects to understand the UI.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"登录成功！用户名 **yezhijun（叶枝君）**，能看到项目列表和权限级别。让我看看成员管理页面长什么样："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_9bNRDGVWq62uUxfVdjir2939","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\inspect_gitlab_members.mjs","content":"import { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\n\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(fileURLToPath(import.meta.url));\nconst WS_DIR = path.resolve(__dirname, '..');\nconst cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(path.join(WS_DIR, 'gitlab_cookies.json'), 'utf8'));\nconst GITLAB = 'https://git.devcloud.ztgame.com';\n\nconst browser = await chromium.launch({ headless: false, args: ['--no-sandbox', '--disable-blink-features=AutomationControlled'] });\nconst context = await browser.newContext({ userAgent: 'Mozilla/5.0' });\nawait context.addInitScript(() => Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'webdriver', { get: () => undefined }));\nawait context.addCookies(cookies);\nconst page = await context.newPage();\n\n// 先看 yyzy_proj/1v1/config 项目的成员页（我们有 Maintainer 权限）\nconst projectPath = 'yyzy_proj/1v1/config';\nconsole.log('Project:', projectPath);\n\n// 尝试 GitLab 的成员管理 API\n// 先获取项目 ID\nconst apiResult = await page.evaluate(async ({ path }) => {\n  const r = await fetch(`/api/v4/projects?search=${encodeURIComponent(path)}`, {\n    headers: { 'Accept': 'application/json' }\n  });\n  if (!r.ok) return 'API error: ' + r.status;\n  return await r.text();\n}, { path: projectPath });\n\nconst data = JSON.parse(apiResult);\nconst project = Array.isArray(data) ? data[0] : data;\nconsole.log('\\nProject info:', JSON.stringify(project, null, 2).substring(0, 500));\n\nconst projectId = project?.id;\nif (projectId) {\n  console.log(`\\nProject ID: ${projectId}`);\n  \n  // 获取项目成员\n  const membersResult = await page.evaluate(async ({ pid }) => {\n    const r = await fetch(`/api/v4/projects/${pid}/members/all?per_page=50`, {\n      headers: { 'Accept': 'application/json' }\n    });\n    if (!r.ok) return 'error: ' + r.status;\n    return await r.text();\n  }, { pid: projectId });\n  \n  try {\n    const members = JSON.parse(membersResult);\n    console.log('\\nMembers:');\n    members.forEach(m => {\n      const role = ['', 'Guest', 'Reporter', 'Developer', 'Maintainer', 'Owner'][m.access_level] || m.access_level;\n      console.log(`  ${m.name} (@${m.username}) - ${role}`);\n    });\n  } catch(e) {\n    console.log('Members parse error:', membersResult.substring(0, 300));\n  }\n\n  // 查看 API 添加成员的格式\n  const addMemberTest = await page.evaluate(async ({ pid }) => {\n    // 只是测试 POST 格式，不真的执行\n    const body = new URLSearchParams();\n    body.append('user_id', '123');\n    body.append('access_level', '30'); // 30=Developer\n    return `POST /api/v4/projects/${pid}/members\\nbody: ${body.toString()}`;\n  }, { pid: projectId });\n  console.log('\\nAdd member API format:', addMemberTest);\n\n  // 试试删除成员的 API 格式\n  console.log(`\\nRemove member API: DELETE /api/v4/projects/${projectId}/members/{user_id}`);\n  \n  // 搜索用户 API\n  const searchUser = await page.evaluate(async () => {\n    const r = await fetch('/api/v4/users?search=周以天&per_page=5', {\n      headers: { 'Accept': 'application/json' }\n    });\n    if (!r.ok) return 'error: ' + r.status;\n    return await r.text();\n  }, { });\n  console.log('\\nSearch \"周以天\":', searchUser.substring(0, 300));\n}\n\nawait browser.close();\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1099,"output":1205,"cacheRead":211072,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":213376,"cost":{"input":0.00015386000000000002,"output":0.0003374,"cacheRead":0.005910016,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.006401276}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779281893502,"responseId":"4e2fdd94-2ae6-4653-904c-03cdcdb55258"}}
