{"type":"message","id":"dc5444de","parentId":"2057eeb2","timestamp":"2026-05-20T12:59:28.643Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Excellent! Now I have the full picture:\n\n1. GitLab API is fully accessible with cookies\n2. I can manage members for projects where I have Maintainer/Owner access\n3. Key user IDs found:\n   - 周以天 (@v-zhouyitian) id=1003\n   - 陈霄豪 (@chenxiaohao) id=1134\n   - 叶枝君 (@yezhijun) id=983\n\n4. Permission levels:\n   - 10 = Guest\n   - 20 = Reporter\n   - 30 = Developer\n   - 40 = Maintainer\n   - 50 = Owner\n\n5. Projects I can manage (Maintainer+): 10 projects including:\n   - yyzy_proj/1v1/config (id=5058)\n   - yyzy/develop_client/nightoffullmoon (id=2751) - which is the main project!\n   - yyzy_proj/gordian/gameconfig (id=4710)\n\nNow I need to save this as a skill so I can manage Git permissions. Let me create the skill and update memory.\n\nThe key commands:\n- Add member: `POST /api/v4/projects/:id/members` with `user_id` and `access_level`\n- Remove member: `DELETE /api/v4/projects/:id/members/:user_id`\n- Update member: `PUT /api/v4/projects/:id/members/:user_id` with `access_level`\n- List members: `GET /api/v4/projects/:id/members/all`\n- Search users: `GET /api/v4/users?search=name`","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"拿到了！信息齐全了。现在创建 Skill："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_LJkpYCfWgCoYHRorlU9c9341","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p ~/.openclaw/plugin-skills/gitlab-permission/scripts"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1054,"output":420,"cacheRead":219008,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":220482,"cost":{"input":0.00014756,"output":0.00011760000000000001,"cacheRead":0.0061322239999999995,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.006397384}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779281964536,"responseId":"1c437517-8689-4f07-9117-1642cf2e3041"}}
{"type":"message","id":"1498b17c","parentId":"dc5444de","timestamp":"2026-05-20T12:59:28.915Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_LJkpYCfWgCoYHRorlU9c9341","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Ŀ¼: C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\plugin-skills\\gitlab-permission\r\n\r\n\r\nMode                 LastWriteTime         Length Name                                                                 \r\n----                 -------------         ------ ----                                                                 \r\nd-----         2026/5/20     20:59                scripts"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":243,"aggregated":"Ŀ¼: C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\plugin-skills\\gitlab-permission\r\n\r\n\r\nMode                 LastWriteTime         Length Name                                                                 \r\n----                 -------------         ------ ----                                                                 \r\nd-----         2026/5/20     20:59                scripts","cwd":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1779281968914}}
{"type":"message","id":"0c93b5a1","parentId":"1498b17c","timestamp":"2026-05-20T12:59:35.142Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me save the data and create the skill. I'll create a management script and a SKILL.md.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_ZzLjh9ymE5Axb1CfZB3f1101","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\plugin-skills\\gitlab-permission\\SKILL.md","content":"---\nname: gitlab-permission\ndescription: 管理 git.devcloud.ztgame.com 上的 GitLab 项目成员权限。支持添加/删除/修改成员，查询项目成员列表。  \n  触发词：git权限、加git权限、管理git、项目成员、gitlab权限。  \n  适用：yyzy_proj 组下的项目，叶枝君账号（Maintainer/Owner 权限）。\n---\n\n# GitLab 权限管理\n\n## 前置条件\n\n- Cookie：`workspace/gitlab_cookies.json`（已保存 _gitlab_session）\n- 仅对叶枝君具有 **Maintainer(40)** 或 **Owner(50)** 权限的项目可操作\n\n## 可管理的项目\n\n| 项目 | ID | 权限 |\n|------|:--:|:----:|\n| yyzy_proj/1v1/config | 5058 | Maintainer |\n| yyzy/develop_client/nightoffullmoon | 2751 | Owner |\n| yyzy_proj/gordian/gameconfig | 4710 | Maintainer |\n| didastudio/cdn_251121 | 5638 | Maintainer |\n| yezhijun1/cdn_solo | 5871 | Owner |\n\n## 权限等级\n\n| 等级 | 名称 | 值 |\n|:----:|------|:--:|\n| 10 | Guest | 访客 |\n| 20 | Reporter | 报告者 |\n| 30 | Developer | 开发者 |\n| 40 | Maintainer | 维护者 |\n| 50 | Owner | 拥有者 |\n\n## 已知用户 ID\n\n| 姓名 | 用户名 | ID |\n|------|--------|:--:|\n| 叶枝君 | @yezhijun | 983 |\n| 周以天 | @v-zhouyitian | 1003 |\n| 陈霄豪 | @chenxiaohao | 1134 |\n\n## API 用法\n\n```javascript\nconst cookieStr = cookies.map(c => `${c.name}=${c.value}`).join('; ');\nconst headers = { 'Cookie': cookieStr, 'Accept': 'application/json' };\nconst GITLAB = 'https://git.devcloud.ztgame.com';\n```\n\n### 查询项目成员\n```bash\nGET /api/v4/projects/{project_id}/members/all?per_page=100\n```\n\n### 添加成员\n```bash\nPOST /api/v4/projects/{project_id}/members\nBody: user_id={user_id}&access_level={10|20|30|40}\n```\n\n### 修改成员权限\n```bash\nPUT /api/v4/projects/{project_id}/members/{user_id}\nBody: access_level={10|20|30|40}\n```\n\n### 删除成员\n```bash\nDELETE /api/v4/projects/{project_id}/members/{user_id}\n```\n\n### 搜索用户\n```bash\nGET /api/v4/users?search={用户名}\n```\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":146,"output":737,"cacheRead":220416,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":221299,"cost":{"input":0.00002044,"output":0.00020636000000000002,"cacheRead":0.006171648,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.006398448}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779281968919,"responseId":"f2c6ebbd-b3fa-4c12-bdd0-905b16eef8f7"}}
