{"type":"message","id":"af6148ef","parentId":"5dc8b6f9","timestamp":"2026-05-20T13:03:25.344Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So:\n1. gameconfig(4710) - Owner(50) ✅\n2. config(5058) - Maintainer(40) ✅\n3. DidaFramework(5048) - Developer(30) - As Developer, I can't add members. Need Maintainer+.\n4. battle1v1(5145) - Not a member ❌\n5. proto(5060) - Not a member ❌\n\nFor repos 3-5, I don't have enough permissions to manage. The user needs to grant me higher access first, or I need to note that only repos where I have Maintainer+ can be managed.\n\nActually wait, the user said \"给我增加我们项目的权限\" meaning they want me to add people to these repos. The user (Yousan) likely has Owner/Maintainer access to all of them. I can use the user's API token/permission to do this... but wait, the cookie is for 叶枝君's account, not Yousan's.\n\nHmm, but 叶枝君 IS Yousan. So the cookie IS the user's session. Let me check what access 叶枝君 has on these repos. 叶枝君 id=983.\n\nFor DidaFramework(5048): 叶枝君 has Developer(30) - can't manage members\nFor battle1v1(5145): 叶枝君 is NOT a member - can't manage\nFor proto(5060): 叶枝君 is NOT a member - can't manage\n\nSo effectively, I can only manage:\n1. gameconfig(4710) - Owner ✅\n2. config(5058) - Maintainer ✅\n\nThe other 3 repos need the user to add 叶枝君 with higher permissions first, OR use a different approach.\n\nActually, let me re-read the user's message. They said \"git权限管理当前只管理这几个仓库\" - so they want me to manage these repos. They probably have the right access via their account. Let me just set up the skill to try all 5 and report which ones succeed/fail.\n\nActually wait - the cookie IS the user's (叶枝君 = Yousan). So if 叶枝君 has Owner on gameconfig and Maintainer on config, that's fine. For the other 3, we just need to note the limitation or the user can grant access.\n\nLet me build the skill with this info and a batch add feature.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_91gd15J8trGh9RXWHESi9004","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\plugin-skills\\gitlab-permission\\SKILL.md","edits":[{"oldText":"## 可管理的项目\n\n| 项目 | ID | 权限 |\n|------|:--:|:----:|\n| yyzy_proj/1v1/config | 5058 | Maintainer |\n| yyzy/develop_client/nightoffullmoon | 2751 | Owner |\n| yyzy_proj/gordian/gameconfig | 4710 | Maintainer |\n| didastudio/cdn_251121 | 5638 | Maintainer |\n| yezhijun1/cdn_solo | 5871 | Owner |","newText":"## 管理的项目组（5 个核心仓库）\n\n当说「给 XX 加项目权限」时，以下 5 个仓库全部加 Developer(30)：\n\n| # | 仓库 | ID | 我的权限 |\n|:-:|------|:--:|:--------:|\n| 1 | yyzy_proj/1v1/config | 5058 | Maintainer ✅ |\n| 2 | yyzy_proj/gordian/gameconfig | 4710 | Owner ✅ |\n| 3 | yyzy_proj/framework/DidaFramework | 5048 | Developer ❌ 无权管理 |\n| 4 | yyzy_proj/1v1/battle1v1 | 5145 | 非成员 ❌ 无权管理 |\n| 5 | yyzy_proj/1v1/proto | 5060 | 非成员 ❌ 无权管理 |\n\n> 注：仓库 3-5 需要主人先给叶枝君提升到 Maintainer 权限才能管理。\n\n## 其他可管理的项目\n\n| 项目 | ID | 权限 |\n|------|:--:|:----:|\n| yyzy/develop_client/nightoffullmoon | 2751 | Owner |\n| didastudio/cdn_251121 | 5638 | Maintainer |\n| yezhijun1/cdn_solo | 5871 | Owner |"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":77,"output":1062,"cacheRead":229504,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":230643,"cost":{"input":0.00001078,"output":0.00029736000000000004,"cacheRead":0.0064261119999999994,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.006734252}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779282195442,"responseId":"82d83e07-af80-44a6-9a1a-e4407b082f73"}}
