{"type":"message","id":"c3e61c20","parentId":"248b8815","timestamp":"2026-05-20T13:03:56.428Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"搞定了 ✅ 现在说「给XX加项目权限」时：\n\n1. 搜索用户找到对应 ID\n2. 批量给 5 个核心仓库加 Developer(30)：\n   - `yyzy_proj/1v1/config`\n   - `yyzy_proj/gordian/gameconfig`\n   - `yyzy_proj/framework/DidaFramework`\n   - `yyzy_proj/1v1/battle1v1`\n   - `yyzy_proj/1v1/proto`\n\n如果某个仓库已加过或权限不够，会提示跳过/失败，不影响其他的。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":55,"output":132,"cacheRead":234112,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":234299,"cost":{"input":0.0000077,"output":0.000036960000000000005,"cacheRead":0.006555136,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.006599796}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779282234091,"responseId":"f175403f-2877-4d74-8265-b2e7ba247ed2"}}
