{"type":"message","id":"4d82ed02","parentId":"7fe0d4ab","timestamp":"2026-05-20T13:26:05.947Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Wait, there's a problem. The `-` characters in the border are ASCII (1 cell wide), but the Chinese characters are 2 cells wide. So the border `+--...--+` might not align properly with the data rows `| 人 | ... |`.\n\nLet me think about this carefully:\n\nData row: `| ` + pad(sender, nw) + ` | ` + pad(type, tw) + ` | ` + pad(result, rw) + ` |`\n- The `|` chars are at fixed positions\n- Between `|` and the next `|`: space(1) + pad(sender, nw_visual) + space(1) = 2 + nw cells\n- The actual visual cells between vertical bars = nw + 2\n\nBorder row: `|` + `-`.repeat(nw + 2) + `|`\n- Between `|` and next `|`: `-`.repeat(nw+2) = nw + 2 dashes\n- Each dash is 1 cell wide, so total = nw + 2 cells\n\nThis should match! The data row has (1 space + sender with nw visual + 1 space) = nw + 2 cells between `|` bars, and the border has nw + 2 dashes between `+` bars.\n\nThe `+` characters at corners: `+` + `-`.repeat(nw+2) + `+` + `-`.repeat(tw+2) + `+` + `-`.repeat(rw+2) + `+`\n\nThis should work! Let me test.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_LXF2gU8ClbL4Bq3z9bwV7220","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node scripts/log_operation.mjs \"更新测试服\" \"兵王\" \"热更\" \"成功\"","timeout":5000,"workdir":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":114,"output":463,"cacheRead":255744,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":256321,"cost":{"input":0.00001596,"output":0.00012964,"cacheRead":0.007160832,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.007306432}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779283559554,"responseId":"fbf12efd-0016-4cf4-aa9b-b1e910869aa9"}}
