{"type":"message","id":"84fbd641","parentId":"4f57c2f2","timestamp":"2026-05-20T13:26:46.350Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_tWpoSaiEuiwVODe84d2m3166","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/**\n * 飞书群消息发送工具\n * 使用 OpenClaw 配置的 appId/appSecret 获取 tenant_access_token 后发送消息\n */\n\nconst APP_ID = 'cli_a9458ff380b99ccb';\nconst APP_SECRET = 'Qs3NVp…OGKv';\n\nasync function getTenantAccessToken() {\n  const res = await fetch('https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal', {\n    method: 'POST',\n    headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },\n    body: JSON.stringify({ app_id: APP_ID, app_secret: APP_SECRET }),\n  });\n  const data = await res.json();\n  if (data.code !== 0) throw new Error(`Get token failed: ${JSON.stringify(data)}`);\n  return data.tenant_access_token;\n}\n\n/**\n * 发送飞书群消息（富文本，支持 @ 提及）\n * @param {string} chatId - 群 chat_id，如 oc_xxx\n * @param {string} text - 消息文本（支持 <at user_id=\"xxx\">name</at> 格式）\n */\nexport async function sendGroupMessage(chatId, text) {\n  const token = await getTenantAccessToken();\n\n  const res = await fetch('https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/im/v1/messages?receive_id_type=chat_id', {\n    method: 'POST',\n    headers: {\n      'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n      'Authorization': `Bearer ${token}`,\n    },\n    body: JSON.stringify({\n      receive_id: chatId,\n      msg_type: 'text',\n      content: JSON.stringify({ text }),\n    }),\n  });\n\n  const data = await res.json();\n  if (data.code !== 0) throw new Error(`Send message failed: ${JSON.stringify(data)}`);\n  return data.data?.message_id;\n}\n\n// 预设消息模板（避免命令行引号转义问题）\nconst TEMPLATES = {\n  'hotupdate-ok': '热更已完成，测试服已更新 ✅ <at user_id=\"ou_348eeddd81d4c03865f9f1684fce6966\">兵王(周以天)</at>',\n  'hotupdate-fail': '❌ 热更流水线失败，请检查日志',\n};\n\n// 直接运行时的入口\nconst chatId = process.argv[2] || 'oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77';\nconst rawText = process.argv[3] || 'hotupdate-ok';\n// 支持模板名或直接文本，并将字面 \\n 转换为真实换行\nconst text = (TEMPLATES[rawText] ?? rawText).replace(/\\\\n/g, '\\n');\n\nsendGroupMessage(chatId, text)\n  .then(msgId => {\n    console.log('发送成功！message_id:', msgId);\n  })\n  .catch(e => {\n    console.error('发送失败:', e.message);\n    process.exit(1);\n  });\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1779283606349}}
{"type":"message","id":"ead255d6","parentId":"84fbd641","timestamp":"2026-05-20T13:26:59.627Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The current script only supports `msg_type: 'text'`. To send interactive cards, I need to use `msg_type: 'interactive'` and provide a card JSON. Let me create a new script that sends the operation log as a Feishu interactive card with a table.\n\nFeishu interactive card format for tables uses `components` with `table` type. The card JSON format is like:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"config\": { \"wide_screen_mode\": true },\n  \"header\": {\n    \"title\": { \"tag\": \"plain_text\", \"content\": \"最近操作日志\" },\n    \"template\": \"blue\"\n  },\n  \"elements\": [\n    {\n      \"tag\": \"column_set\",\n      \"flex_mode\": \"none\",\n      \"background_style\": \"default\",\n      \"columns\": [\n        {\n          \"tag\": \"column\",\n          \"width\": \"weighted\",\n          \"weight\": 1,\n          \"vertical_align\": \"center\",\n          \"elements\": [{ \"tag\": \"plain_text\", \"content\": \"人\" }]\n        },\n        ...\n      ]\n    },\n    ...\n  ]\n}\n```\n\nActually, for a simple table in Feishu card, I can use `div` elements with `column_set` for headers and rows. But this is complex.\n\nA simpler approach for Feishu interactive card: use Markdown-like content in a `div` element with `text` tag. Actually Feishu card supports `markdown` in `div` elements.\n\nLet me create a simple card with a table rendered using markdown within a Feishu card message.\n\nActually, the simplest approach might be to use msg_type: 'interactive' with a card that has a div with markdown table content. But Feishu cards don't render markdown tables.\n\nLet me use a different approach: use `msg_type: 'post'` (rich text) which supports tables. Or use `msg_type: 'interactive'` with `column_set` elements.\n\nActually, the simplest approach for a clean table: use `msg_type: 'interactive'` with a card that lists each log entry as a separate row in a `column_set`.\n\nLet me write a new script `feishu_send_log_card.mjs` that sends the log as a card.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_DUEtq56MVdAXhxToleJU8928","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\feishu_send_log_card.mjs","content":"/**\n * 发送操作日志飞书卡片（Interactive Card 格式，带表格）\n */\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\n\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(fileURLToPath(import.meta.url));\nconst WS = path.resolve(__dirname, '..');\nconst LOG_FILE = path.join(WS, 'memory', 'operation-log.json');\n\nconst APP_ID = 'cli_a9458ff380b99ccb';\nconst APP_SECRET = 'Qs3NVpgH7h4UP7cVPfZRHh72E3jEOGKv';\n\nasync function getToken() {\n  const r = await fetch('https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal', {\n    method: 'POST',\n    headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },\n    body: JSON.stringify({ app_id: APP_ID, app_secret: APP_SECRET }),\n  });\n  const d = await r.json();\n  if (d.code !== 0) throw new Error(`Token failed: ${JSON.stringify(d)}`);\n  return d.tenant_access_token;\n}\n\nfunction makeCard(logs) {\n  // 构造表头行\n  const headerRow = {\n    \"tag\": \"column_set\",\n    \"flex_mode\": \"none\",\n    \"background_style\": \"grey\",\n    \"columns\": [\n      { \"tag\": \"column\", \"width\": \"weighted\", \"weight\": 2, \"vertical_align\": \"center\",\n        \"elements\": [{ \"tag\": \"plain_text\", \"content\": \"人\" }] },\n      { \"tag\": \"column\", \"width\": \"weighted\", \"weight\": 2, \"vertical_align\": \"center\",\n        \"elements\": [{ \"tag\": \"plain_text\", \"content\": \"事情\" }] },\n      { \"tag\": \"column\", \"width\": \"weighted\", \"weight\": 2, \"vertical_align\": \"center\",\n        \"elements\": [{ \"tag\": \"plain_text\", \"content\": \"详情\" }] },\n      { \"tag\": \"column\", \"width\": \"weighted\", \"weight\": 1, \"vertical_align\": \"center\",\n        \"elements\": [{ \"tag\": \"plain_text\", \"content\": \"结果\" }] },\n    ]\n  };\n\n  // 数据行\n  const dataRows = logs.slice(-5).reverse().map(l => ({\n    \"tag\": \"column_set\",\n    \"flex_mode\": \"none\",\n    \"background_style\": \"default\",\n    \"columns\": [\n      { \"tag\": \"column\", \"width\": \"weighted\", \"weight\": 2, \"vertical_align\": \"center\",\n        \"elements\": [{ \"tag\": \"lark_md\", \"content\": l.sender }] },\n      { \"tag\": \"column\", \"width\": \"weighted\", \"weight\": 2, \"vertical_align\": \"center\",\n        \"elements\": [{ \"tag\": \"lark_md\", \"content\": l.type }] },\n      { \"tag\": \"column\", \"width\": \"weighted\", \"weight\": 2, \"vertical_align\": \"center\",\n        \"elements\": [{ \"tag\": \"lark_md\", \"content\": l.detail || '-' }] },\n      { \"tag\": \"column\", \"width\": \"weighted\", \"weight\": 1, \"vertical_align\": \"center\",\n        \"elements\": [{ \"tag\": \"lark_md\", \"content\": l.result || '-' }] },\n    ]\n  }));\n\n  return {\n    \"config\": { \"wide_screen_mode\": true },\n    \"header\": {\n      \"title\": { \"tag\": \"plain_text\", \"content\": `📋 最近 ${logs.length <= 5 ? logs.length : 5} 条操作日志` },\n      \"template\": \"blue\"\n    },\n    \"elements\": [headerRow, ...dataRows]\n  };\n}\n\nconst chatId = process.argv[2] || 'oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77';\n\nconst logs = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(LOG_FILE, 'utf8'));\nconst card = makeCard(logs);\n\nconst token = await getToken();\nconst r = await fetch('https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/im/v1/messages?receive_id_type=chat_id', {\n  method: 'POST',\n  headers: {\n    'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n    'Authorization': `Bearer ${token}`,\n  },\n  body: JSON.stringify({\n    receive_id: chatId,\n    msg_type: 'interactive',\n    content: JSON.stringify(card),\n  }),\n});\n\nconst d = await r.json();\nif (d.code === 0) {\n  console.log('✅ 卡片已发送');\n} else {\n  console.error('❌ 发送失败:', JSON.stringify(d));\n}\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":739,"output":1625,"cacheRead":257792,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":260156,"cost":{"input":0.00010346,"output":0.00045500000000000006,"cacheRead":0.007218176,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.007776636}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779283606355,"responseId":"78db52e6-de08-4164-8b30-d7301dc67e10"}}
