{"type":"message","id":"f4b08869","parentId":"e446cbdb","timestamp":"2026-05-20T13:29:04.588Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user says the columns don't have borders, only rows have dividers. Feishu's column_set doesn't support column borders natively. Let me try a different approach - instead of using column_set, I can use a table-like layout with markdown. \n\nActually, looking at the Feishu card capabilities more carefully, there's no built-in table component that supports column borders. The `column_set` just lays out content side by side without visible column borders.\n\nAlternative approaches:\n1. Use a single `div` with markdown table text - Feishu's lark_md might support markdown tables\n2. Use `hr` elements to separate everything\n3. Try a completely different card layout\n\nLet me try option 1 - see if markdown tables work in lark_md content.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"飞书卡片 column_set 没有列边框功能。换个思路——用 Markdown 表格渲染："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_1MzBKB2eF7i9Nh6LeVVD4770","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\feishu_send_log_card.mjs","content":"/**\n * 发送操作日志飞书卡片（Markdown 表格形式）\n */\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\n\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(fileURLToPath(import.meta.url));\nconst WS = path.resolve(__dirname, '..');\nconst LOG_FILE = path.join(WS, 'memory', 'operation-log.json');\n\nconst APP_ID = 'cli_a9458ff380b99ccb';\nconst APP_SECRET = 'Qs3NVpgH7h4UP7cVPfZRHh72E3jEOGKv';\n\nasync function getToken() {\n  const r = await fetch('https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal', {\n    method: 'POST', headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },\n    body: JSON.stringify({ app_id: APP_ID, app_secret: APP_SECRET }),\n  });\n  const d = await r.json();\n  if (d.code !== 0) throw new Error('Token failed');\n  return d.tenant_access_token;\n}\n\nfunction makeCard(logs) {\n  const recent = logs.slice(-5).reverse();\n  // 用 Markdown 表格\n  let md = '| 人 | 事情 | 详情 | 结果 |\\n| --- | --- | --- | --- |\\n';\n  recent.forEach(l => {\n    md += `| ${l.sender} | ${l.type} | ${l.detail || '-'} | ${l.result || '-'} |\\n`;\n  });\n\n  return {\n    config: { wide_screen_mode: true },\n    header: { title: { tag: 'plain_text', content: `最近 ${recent.length} 条操作日志` }, template: 'blue' },\n    elements: [{ tag: 'div', text: { tag: 'lark_md', content: md } }],\n  };\n}\n\nconst targetId = process.argv[2] || 'oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77';\nconst targetType = process.argv[3] === 'user' ? 'open_id' : 'chat_id';\n\nconst logs = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(LOG_FILE, 'utf8'));\nconst card = makeCard(logs);\nconst token = await getToken();\n\nconst r = await fetch(`https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/im/v1/messages?receive_id_type=${targetType}`, {\n  method: 'POST',\n  headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json', Authorization: `Bearer ${token}` },\n  body: JSON.stringify({ receive_id: targetId, msg_type: 'interactive', content: JSON.stringify(card) }),\n});\n\nconst d = await r.json();\nconsole.log(d.code === 0 ? '卡片已发送 ✓' : '发送失败: ' + JSON.stringify(d));\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":3745,"output":895,"cacheRead":262144,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":266784,"cost":{"input":0.0005243,"output":0.0002506,"cacheRead":0.007340032,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.008114932}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779283737059,"responseId":"4101586e-9ef4-4f17-83c3-f3f38bd69a5d"}}
