{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6fef3da944a4b3656860acc5706\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yousan(叶枝君)\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-05-20 21:29 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yousan(叶枝君) (ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"name\": \"Yousan(叶枝君)\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"cf4cb3bf","parentId":"abff0f8f","timestamp":"2026-05-20T13:29:30.332Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"f2a35879","parentId":"cf4cb3bf","timestamp":"2026-05-20T13:29:45.721Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants the card format (interactive card) with proper column borders. Since Feishu's column_set doesn't support column borders, let me think of another approach.\n\nLooking at the Feishu card template documentation more carefully, I could try:\n\n1. Using `column_set` with a more styled approach - maybe adding background colors to individual columns\n2. Using individual `div` elements per cell with explicit borders\n\nActually, there's a better approach. I can create a table-like layout using multiple `column_set` elements where each column in the set has a grey background, giving the appearance of borders. Or I can use `div` with `extra` styling.\n\nWait, Feishu cards don't support CSS styling on div/column elements. The only styling available is:\n- `background_style` on `column_set`: 'default' or 'grey'\n- Text formatting via `lark_md`\n\nActually, looking at the Feishu card API more carefully, there might be a way to use `column_set` with `column` having a background. Let me check if I can use a different approach...\n\nActually, I think the best approach is to use `column_set` with alternating grey backgrounds for columns, which gives the appearance of column separators. Or I could put each column's content in its own `div` with a `column_set` wrapper.\n\nBut actually, the user originally liked card format and just wanted borders. The `column_set` with `hr` between rows was close. Let me try adding a thin vertical separator by using `div` within each column cell that looks like it has borders.\n\nActually, I just realized - I can use nested `column_set` with `hr` for both column and row separators. But Feishu cards are limited.\n\nWait, there's another approach: use the `table` component. Let me check... Feishu cards don't have a native `table` component. But there's an `action` component...\n\nLet me just go back to the column_set + hr approach which already looked decent, and try to add column borders by putting each column's content in a `note` or `div` with lark_md content that includes border characters.\n\nActually, the simplest thing I can do: go back to the column_set approach (which the user said was \"还可以\"), but try putting a thin vertical bar between columns by adding `|` characters in the markdown. For example:\n\nColumn 1: `**人**`  \nColumn 2: `| **事情**`\nColumn 3: `| **详情**`\nColumn 4: `| **结果**`\n\nThis would visually show `人 | 事情 | 详情 | 结果` with `|` acting as column borders.\n\nLet me try this approach.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"回到卡片样式，在每列内容前加 `│` 来实现列分割："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_tS7csAnTDXuHlqll21Y91116","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\feishu_send_log_card.mjs","content":"/**\n * 发送操作日志飞书卡片（column_set + 竖线分隔）\n */\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\n\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(fileURLToPath(import.meta.url));\nconst WS = path.resolve(__dirname, '..');\nconst LOG_FILE = path.join(WS, 'memory', 'operation-log.json');\n\nconst APP_ID = 'cli_a9458ff380b99ccb';\nconst APP_SECRET = 'Qs3NVpgH7h4UP7cVPfZRHh72E3jEOGKv';\n\nasync function getToken() {\n  const r = await fetch('https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal', {\n    method: 'POST', headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },\n    body: JSON.stringify({ app_id: APP_ID, app_secret: APP_SECRET }),\n  });\n  const d = await r.json();\n  if (d.code !== 0) throw new Error('Token failed');\n  return d.tenant_access_token;\n}\n\nfunction t(text) {\n  return { tag: 'div', text: { tag: 'lark_md', content: text } };\n}\nfunction col(text, w) {\n  return { tag: 'column', width: 'weighted', weight: w, vertical_align: 'center', elements: [t(text)] };\n}\n\nfunction makeCard(logs) {\n  const recent = logs.slice(-5).reverse();\n\n  const header = {\n    tag: 'column_set', flex_mode: 'none', background_style: 'grey',\n    columns: [\n      col('**人**', 2),\n      col('**│ 事情**', 2),\n      col('**│ 详情**', 3),\n      col('**│ 结果**', 1),\n    ],\n  };\n\n  const hr = { tag: 'hr' };\n  const rows = recent.map(l => ({\n    tag: 'column_set', flex_mode: 'none', background_style: 'default',\n    columns: [\n      col(l.sender, 2),\n      col(`│ ${l.type}`, 2),\n      col(`│ ${l.detail || '-'}`, 3),\n      col(`│ ${l.result || '-'}`, 1),\n    ],\n  }));\n\n  // 交错行之间放分隔线\n  const elements = [header, hr];\n  rows.forEach((r, i) => {\n    if (i > 0) elements.push(hr);\n    elements.push(r);\n  });\n\n  return {\n    config: { wide_screen_mode: true },\n    header: { title: { tag: 'plain_text', content: `最近 ${recent.length} 条操作日志` }, template: 'blue' },\n    elements,\n  };\n}\n\nconst targetId = process.argv[2] || 'oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77';\nconst targetType = process.argv[3] === 'user' ? 'open_id' : 'chat_id';\nconst logs = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(LOG_FILE, 'utf8'));\nconst card = makeCard(logs);\nconst token = await getToken();\n\nconst r = await fetch(`https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/im/v1/messages?receive_id_type=${targetType}`, {\n  method: 'POST',\n  headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json', Authorization: `Bearer ${token}` },\n  body: JSON.stringify({ receive_id: targetId, msg_type: 'interactive', content: JSON.stringify(card) }),\n});\n\nconst d = await r.json();\nconsole.log(d.code === 0 ? '卡片已发送 ✓' : '发送失败: ' + JSON.stringify(d));\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2493,"output":1497,"cacheRead":264576,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":268566,"cost":{"input":0.00034902,"output":0.00041916,"cacheRead":0.007408128,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.008176308}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779283770332,"responseId":"87c86d71-91f2-4ad6-a9a5-eaa5945a39e1"}}
