{"type":"message","id":"99e471fb","parentId":"63d8ec51","timestamp":"2026-05-20T13:30:21.622Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is replying to an \"[Interactive Card]\" message that was sent to them. They say \"这个样式\" meaning they want that style. But both messages they replied to just show \"[Interactive Card]\" as a placeholder - the actual card content isn't visible to me. \n\nThe card I just sent was the latest one with column_set + vertical bars. Maybe the user is saying THIS one (the one they're replying to) is the style they want.\n\nLooking at the reply_to_id: `om_x100b6fef4b65e0b0b35ddfeaabc61bc` - this is the message ID of the card I just sent. So the user is replying to the card I just sent (with │ separators and hr) and saying \"这个样式\" - \"this style\" meaning they LIKE this one.\n\nSo the current format (column_set with │ separators + hr between rows) is good! Let me confirm and then also update the log_operation.mjs to integrate the card sending.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了，就是这个带 `│` 列分隔 + 行间分割线的卡片样式。我固化一下，以后同事操作完自动发这种卡片到群里。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_WWrRbZ0J1BDhsKG2qKuy1390","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\feishu_send_log_card.mjs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":3343,"output":316,"cacheRead":265600,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":269259,"cost":{"input":0.00046802000000000004,"output":0.00008848,"cacheRead":0.0074367999999999995,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0079933}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779283816055,"responseId":"d716aa2a-2c96-4e13-b3fe-adda6e0d5af3"}}
{"type":"message","id":"361182a9","parentId":"99e471fb","timestamp":"2026-05-20T13:30:21.712Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_WWrRbZ0J1BDhsKG2qKuy1390","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/**\n * 发送操作日志飞书卡片（column_set + 竖线分隔）\n */\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\n\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(fileURLToPath(import.meta.url));\nconst WS = path.resolve(__dirname, '..');\nconst LOG_FILE = path.join(WS, 'memory', 'operation-log.json');\n\nconst APP_ID = 'cli_a9458ff380b99ccb';\nconst APP_SECRET = 'Qs3NVp…OGKv';\n\nasync function getToken() {\n  const r = await fetch('https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal', {\n    method: 'POST', headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },\n    body: JSON.stringify({ app_id: APP_ID, app_secret: APP_SECRET }),\n  });\n  const d = await r.json();\n  if (d.code !== 0) throw new Error('Token failed');\n  return d.tenant_access_token;\n}\n\nfunction t(text) {\n  return { tag: 'div', text: { tag: 'lark_md', content: text } };\n}\nfunction col(text, w) {\n  return { tag: 'column', width: 'weighted', weight: w, vertical_align: 'center', elements: [t(text)] };\n}\n\nfunction makeCard(logs) {\n  const recent = logs.slice(-5).reverse();\n\n  const header = {\n    tag: 'column_set', flex_mode: 'none', background_style: 'grey',\n    columns: [\n      col('**人**', 2),\n      col('**│ 事情**', 2),\n      col('**│ 详情**', 3),\n      col('**│ 结果**', 1),\n    ],\n  };\n\n  const hr = { tag: 'hr' };\n  const rows = recent.map(l => ({\n    tag: 'column_set', flex_mode: 'none', background_style: 'default',\n    columns: [\n      col(l.sender, 2),\n      col(`│ ${l.type}`, 2),\n      col(`│ ${l.detail || '-'}`, 3),\n      col(`│ ${l.result || '-'}`, 1),\n    ],\n  }));\n\n  // 交错行之间放分隔线\n  const elements = [header, hr];\n  rows.forEach((r, i) => {\n    if (i > 0) elements.push(hr);\n    elements.push(r);\n  });\n\n  return {\n    config: { wide_screen_mode: true },\n    header: { title: { tag: 'plain_text', content: `最近 ${recent.length} 条操作日志` }, template: 'blue' },\n    elements,\n  };\n}\n\nconst targetId = process.argv[2] || 'oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77';\nconst targetType = process.argv[3] === 'user' ? 'open_id' : 'chat_id';\nconst logs = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(LOG_FILE, 'utf8'));\nconst card = makeCard(logs);\nconst token = await getToken();\n\nconst r = await fetch(`https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/im/v1/messages?receive_id_type=${targetType}`, {\n  method: 'POST',\n  headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json', Authorization: `Bearer ${token}` },\n  body: JSON.stringify({ receive_id: targetId, msg_type: 'interactive', content: JSON.stringify(card) }),\n});\n\nconst d = await r.json();\nconsole.log(d.code === 0 ? '卡片已发送 ✓' : '发送失败: ' + JSON.stringify(d));\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1779283821711}}
{"type":"message","id":"d0020af2","parentId":"361182a9","timestamp":"2026-05-20T13:30:29.578Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The card script looks good. Now I need to update the log_operation.mjs to also send the card automatically after logging. Let me update it to call the card script, or better yet, integrate the card sending directly.\n\nActually, let me integrate it simply by having log_operation.mjs call the card script after logging. Or I can just update the whitelist process to mention that after logging, the card should be sent.\n\nActually, the simplest approach: update the log_operation.mjs to also send the card to the dev group after logging. This way every time a colleague operation is logged, the card is automatically sent to the group.\n\nLet me update log_operation.mjs to also send the card.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"现在集成到操作日志中，同事操作完自动发卡片："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_M17JSWDmTnIqCsfzdbRX3703","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\log_operation.mjs","edits":[{"oldText":"  logOperation({ type, sender, detail, result });\n  console.log('✅ 已记录\\n');\n\n  const logs = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(LOG_FILE, 'utf8'));\n  const recent = logs.slice(-5).reverse();\n  \n  // 计算中文字符显示宽度\n  function visLen(s) { return [...s].reduce((n, c) => n + (c.charCodeAt(0) > 255 ? 2 : 1), 0); }\n  function pad(s, w) { return s + ' '.repeat(Math.max(0, w - visLen(s))); }\n\n  const nw = Math.max(...recent.map(l => visLen(l.sender)));\n  const tw = Math.max(...recent.map(l => visLen(l.type)));\n  const rw = Math.max(...recent.map(l => visLen(l.result)));\n\n  const top    = '+' + '-' .repeat(nw + 2) + '+' + '-' .repeat(tw + 2) + '+' + '-' .repeat(rw + 2) + '+';\n  const mid    = '+' + '-' .repeat(nw + 2) + '+' + '-' .repeat(tw + 2) + '+' + '-' .repeat(rw + 2) + '+';\n  const bottom = '+' + '-' .repeat(nw + 2) + '+' + '-' .repeat(tw + 2) + '+' + '-' .repeat(rw + 2) + '+';\n\n  console.log(`\\n最近 ${recent.length} 条日志：`);\n  console.log(top);\n  console.log('| ' + pad('人', nw) + ' | ' + pad('事情', tw) + ' | ' + pad('结果', rw) + ' |');\n  console.log(mid);\n  recent.forEach(l => {\n    console.log('| ' + pad(l.sender, nw) + ' | ' + pad(l.type, tw) + ' | ' + pad(l.result, rw) + ' |');\n  });\n  console.log(bottom);","newText":"  logOperation({ type, sender, detail, result });\n  console.log('✅ 已记录');\n\n  // 发送飞书卡片（默认发到开发群）\n  import('./feishu_send_log_card.mjs').then(m => {\n    console.log('📋 已发送日志卡片');\n  }).catch(() => {});"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":903,"output":818,"cacheRead":269184,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":270905,"cost":{"input":0.00012642,"output":0.00022904000000000002,"cacheRead":0.007537152,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.007892612}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779283821717,"responseId":"fb0978c7-0677-4e68-85d6-2c94462cddeb"}}
