{"type":"message","id":"5c7cf1f2","parentId":"ba3858ef","timestamp":"2026-05-20T13:33:30.046Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me append the final updates to today's memory.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_rifPbd13Yw5oISmswRiV9887","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\\2026-05-20.md","edits":[{"oldText":"## Context 状态\n- 本 session 接近满载（212k/200k），预压缩记忆已 flush","newText":"## QA 处理人规则更新\n- QA 子需求处理人改为：刘俊鹏;周以天（脚本硬追加周以天）\n- 其他预设处理人：客户端=叶枝君，服务器=胡新雷1，策划=赵乾A;仲伟国\n\n## 母单处理人规则\n- 母单处理人 = 谁让提的单就是谁\n- 通过 `data[Story][owner]` 设置\n- CLI 第四个参数传入\n\n## 单一子需求添加\n- 新增脚本：`add_sub_story.mjs`\n- 不嵌套模板，不加任何预设子工作项\n- 支持 10 种子需求类型：客户端/服务器/策划/QA/UI/UI验收/动作/特效/音频/原画\n\n## GitLab 权限管理 Skill\n- 创建了 Skill：`gitlab-permission`（`~/.openclaw/plugin-skills/gitlab-permission/`）\n- 5 个核心仓库：config(5058)/gameconfig(4710)/DidaFramework(5048)/battle1v1(5145)/proto(5060)\n- 批量添加命令：`node scripts/git_permission.mjs batch <人名> developer`\n- 用户 ID：叶枝君=983，周以天=1003，陈霄豪=1134\n- Cookie：`workspace/gitlab_cookies.json`\n\n## 同事操作日志系统\n- 脚本：`log_operation.mjs` + `feishu_send_log_card.mjs`\n- 每次同事操作完记录日志到 `memory/operation-log.json`\n- 自动发送飞书互动卡片到开发群（column_set + │ 列分隔 + 行间 hr）\n- 卡片格式：编号 | 人 | 事情 | 详情 | 结果\n\n## 反馈格式定型\n- 开单反馈：需求单已经开好了：[标题](链接)\n- 添加子需求反馈：[标题](链接)\n- 日志卡片飞书互动卡片样式确认\n\n## Context 状态\n- 本 session 接近满载（212k/200k），预压缩记忆已 flush"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":562,"output":621,"cacheRead":277504,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":278687,"cost":{"input":0.00007868,"output":0.00017388,"cacheRead":0.007770112,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.008022672}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779284003246,"responseId":"cc768664-f046-40b0-b56e-8aaa4d50c4d2"}}
